%20capital.%C2%A0The%20Air%20Quality%20Index%20(AQI)%20in%20Delhi%20had%20been%20hovering%20around%20the%20215%20mark%20over%20the%20past%20three%20days%2C%20but%20saw%20a%20sharp%20rise%20this%20morning%20due%20to%20the%20bursting%20of%20crackers%2C%20the%20minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20many%20people%20did%20not%20burst%20crackers%2C%20some%20places%20saw%20targeted%20bursting%20of%20crackers.%20People%20of%20Delhi%20had%20in%20mind%20that%20the%20air%20quality%20should%20not%20deteoriorate.%20But%20the%20BJP%20encouraged%20people%20to%20burst%20crackers%2C%20Delhi%20is%20paying%20the%20price.%20If%20crackers%20were%20not%20burst%2C%20Delhi's%20air%20would%20be%20clean%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReal-time%20trends%20on%20air%20quality%20monitors%20clocked%20huge%20jumps%20in%20Delhi's%20air%20pollution%20levels%20as%20the%20sound%20of%20crackers%20rang%20through%20the%20National%20Capital%20Region%20last%20evening.%20According%20to%20data%20recorded%20by%20the%20Central%20Pollution%20Control%20Board%2C%20levels%20of%20pollutants%20PM2.5%20and%20PM10%20saw%20a%20big%20jump%20this%20morning.%20The%20AQI%20this%20morning%20was%20around%20the%20300%20mark%2C%20representing%20'very%20poor'%20air%20quality.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Delhi%20minister%20said%20the%20BJP%20is%20in%20power%20in%20neighbouring%20Haryana%20and%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20and%20at%20the%20centre.%20%26quot%3BDid%20any%20BJP%20leader%20appeal%20to%20people%20not%20to%20burst%20crackers%3F%20It%20is%20unfortunate%20how%20the%20BJP%20did%20not%20fulfill%20its%20responsibility%20despite%20a%20Supreme%20Court%20order%20(banning%20crackers).%20The%20BJP%20wanted%20crackers%20to%20be%20burst.%20The%20result%20is%20before%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Delhi%20Minister%20appealed%20to%20people%20to%20not%20be%20%26quot%3Bmisled%26quot%3B%20by%20the%20BJP.%20Mr%20Rai%20has%20called%20a%20meeting%20this%20afternoon%20to%20discus