%20since%20last%20morning%20as%20the%20air%20quality%20in%20Delhi%20deteriorated%20back%20to%20toxic%20levels%20a%20day%20after%20Diwali.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM2.5%2C%20the%20most%20damaging%20of%20all%20particles%20present%20in%20the%20air%2C%20clocked%20an%20hourly%20average%20of%20200.8%20at%207%20am.%20It%20was%2083.5%20at%20the%20same%20time%20yesterday%2C%20according%20to%20data%20recorded%20by%20the%20Central%20Pollution%20Control%20Board%20(CPCB).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Fhkj30hlo_pm25-diwali_625x300_13_November_23.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20PM2.5%20and%20PM10%20pollutant%20levels%20touched%20500%20at%20most%20places%20during%20this%20period%2C%20including%20in%20Rohini%2C%20ITO%2C%20and%20Delhi%20airport%20area%2C%20showed%20CPCB%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20air%20quality%20index%20(AQI)%20is%20derived%20from%20the%20value%20of%20six%20particulate%20and%20gaseous%20matter%20in%20the%20air.%20Of%20these%2C%20PM%202.5%20is%20the%20main%20factor%20as%20it%20passes%20the%20nose%20and%20throat%20barrier%2C%20goes%20into%20the%20lungs%2C%20gets%20deposited%20there%20and%20gets%20absorbed%20into%20the%20blood%2C%20according%20to%20Dr%20Arvind%20Kumar%2C%20chairman%20of%20Institute%20of%20Chest%20Surgery%20at%20Medanta%20Gurugram.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM2.5%20and%20smaller%20particles%20are%20critical%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20damaging%20lungs%20and%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20body.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDelhi%20yesterday%20witnessed%20its%20best%20Diwali%20day%20air%20quality%20in%20eight%20years%2C%20but%20the%20AQI%20crossed%20500%20at%20most%20places%20this%20morning%20after%20the%20NCR%20region%20witnessed%20a%20widespread%20violation%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court's%20cracker%20ban.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERead%20%7C%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhi-ncr-air-reaches-toxic-high-as-cracker-craze-counters-rain-relief-4569327%5C%22%3EDelhi%20Air%20Crisis%20Worsens%20As%20Diwali%20Fireworks%20Wipe%20Out%20Rain%20Relief%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERealtime%20monitoring%20websites%20showed%20several%20places%2C%20including%20Lajpat%20Nagar%20and%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20Stadium%2C%20reporting%20an%20AQI%20above%20900.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20AQI%20between%20zero%20and%2050%20is%20considered%20'good'%2C%2051%20and%20100%20'satisfactory'%2C%20101%20and%20200%20'moderate'%2C%20201%20and%20300%20'poor'%2C%20301%20and%20400%20'very%20poor'%2C%20401%20and%20450%20'severe'%20and%20above%20450%20'severe%20plus'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESupreme%20Court%20last%20week%20clarified%20that%20its%20order%20banning%20firecrackers%20containing%20barium%20binds%20every%20state%20and%20is%20not%20just%20limited%20to%20the%20Delhi-NCR%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20fire-related%20incidents%20were%20also%20reported%20last%20evening.%20Delhi%20Fire%20Service%20received%20208%20fire-related%20calls%20yesterday%2C%20including%2022%20related%20to%20crackers%2C%20said%20DFS%20chief%20Atul%20Garg.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDelhi%2C%20where%20the%20air%20quality%20ranks%20among%20the%20worst%20in%20the%20world's%20capital%20cities%2C%20was%20cloaked%20in%20a%20thick%20blanket%20of%20smog%20with%20severe%20pollution%20levels%20for%20a%20week%20since%20October%2028.%20The%20government%20had%20to%20shut%20schools%20and%20ban%20diesel%20trucks%20in%20view%20of%20the%20pollution%2C%20though%20it%20stopped%20short%20of%20enforcing%20the%20odd-even%20rule.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20AQI%20stood%20at%20218%20in%20Delhi%20at%204%20pm%20yesterday%2C%20the%20best%20in%20at%20least%20three%20weeks%2C%20with%20rains%20last%20week%20bringing%20about%20a%20slight%20improvement%20just%20ahead%20of%20the%20festival%20of%20lights.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699856940000%2C%22visual%22