Fphoto%2Fmsid-105177848%2Cimgsize-2243022.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fhyderabad%2Fsix-killed-in-fire-at-godown-in-hyderabad%2Farticleshow%2F105177042.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TIMESOFINDIA.COM%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Twist%20In%20Europe's%20Biggest%20Tax%20Fraud%20Case%20Involving%20Indian-Origin%20Tycoon%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EBanks%20in%20the%20UK%20are%20set%20to%20be%20impacted%20by%20a%20tax%20fraud%20scandal%2C%20said%20to%20be%20Europe's%20biggest.%20According%20to%20UK-based%20financial%20website%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thisismoney.co.uk%2Fmoney%2Fmarkets%2Farticle-12737793%2FUK-banks-Europes-biggest-tax-fraud.html%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20Is%20Money%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20'cum-ex'%20tax%20fraud%20is%20worth%2010%20billion%20pounds%20in%20Germany%20alone.%20Nearly%202%2C000%20suspects%20in%20London%20alone%2C%20including%20bankers%2C%20brokers%20and%20hedge%20fund%20managers%2C%20are%20involved%20in%20the%20case%2C%20said%20the%20financial%20website.%20The%20banks%20under%20investigation%20are%20Britain's%20Barclays%2C%20Bank%20of%20America%20Merrill%20Lynch%2C%20Morgan%20Stanley%20of%20the%20US%2C%20France's%20BNP%20and%20Japan's%20Nomura.%20Several%20law%20firms%20and%20auditors%20are%20also%20implicated%2C%20along%20with%20an%20Indian-origin%20tycoon%2C%20who%20lost%20a%20final%20bid%20to%20block%20proceedings%20against%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20least%20half%20a%20dozen%20'cum-ex'%20probes%20were%20started%20in%20Germany%2C%20with%20one%20in%20Cologne%20being%20the%20broadest.%20The%20banks%20say%20they%20are%20cooperating%20with%20prosecutors.%20Investigations%20were%20opened%20in%20other%20countries%20including%20Belgium%20and%20Denmark.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20is%20the%20'cum-ex'%20scam%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20an%20old%20%3Cem%3EWashington%20Post%3C%2Fem%3E%20report%2C%20the%20scam%20was%20essentially%20a%20double-tipping%20strategy%20that%20exploited%20a%20loophole%20in%20the%20tax%20code%2C%20allowing%20multiple%20people%20to%20claim%20ownership%20of%20a%20stock%20and%20claim%20refunds%20on%20dividend%20tax%20that%20was%20only%20paid%20once.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20practice%20was%20named%20after%20the%20Latin%20terms%20cum%2Fex%2C%20meaning%20with%2Fwithout%2C%20because%20the%20stock%20was%20sold%20with%20-%20but%20delivered%20without%20-%20a%20dividend%20payment%2C%20the%20outlet%20further%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20practice%20was%20abolished%20in%20Germany%20in%202012.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhen%20was%20it%20discovered%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.europarl.europa.eu%2Fcmsdata%2F158435%2F2018-11-26%2520-%2520Information%2520paper%2520on%2520Cum-ex%2520-%2520Cum-cum.pdf%5C%22%3EEuropean%20Parliament%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20scandal%20allegedly%20started%20in%202001%20and%20was%20discovered%20in%20Germany%20in%202012.%20A%20massive%20investigation%20was%20launched%20on%20the%20so-called%20'cum-ex%20files'%20by%20European%20media%20outlets%20and%20led%20by%20German%20Correctiv%20group.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOther%20countries%20that%20have%20been%20singed%20by%20the%20scam%20are%20Denmark%2C%20Belgium%2C%20Austria%2C%20Switzerland%20and%20Norway.%20The%20cases%20are%20likely%20to%20continue%20for%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20much%20money%20is%20involved%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20been%20estimated%20that%20the%20total%20costs%20to%20European%20taxpayers%20of%20the%20cum-ex%20schemes%20deployed%20between%202001%20and%202012%20amount%20to%20more%20than%2055%20billion%20euros%20between%202001%20and%202012%2C%20the%20European%20Parliament%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWho%20all%20have%20been%20charged%20or%20convicted%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20MM%20Warburg%20CEO%20Christian%20Olearius%20became%20the%20first%20leading%20banker%20to%20be%20charged%20(in%20July%202022).%20Apart%20from%20this%2C%20German%20tax%20attorney%20Hanno%20Berger%20was%20sentenced%20to%20eight%20years%20after%20being%20extradited%20from%20Switzerland.%20Paul%20Mora%2C%20a%20former%20investment%20banker%20from%20New%20Zealand%20was%20placed%20on%20Interpol's%20Most-Wanted%20list%20in%202021.%20Executives%20of%20London-based%20asset%20manager%20Duet%20Group%20along%20with%20four%20investment%20bankers%20at%20now%20defunct%20Maple%20Bank%20were%20also%20sent%20to%20jail.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHedge%20fund%20founder%20Sanjay%20Shah%20was%20also%20charged%20along%20with%20six%20others%20to%20settle%20their%20German%20money-laundering%20cases%20over%20the%20proceeds%20of%20Cum-Ex%20tax%20deals.%20Last%20week%2C%20Shah%20lost%20the%20final%20bid%20to%20block%20Denmark's%20tax%20authority%20from%20pursuing%20him%20and%20others%20in%20London%20over%20the%20alleged%20tax%20fraud%2C%20after%20senior%20judges%20ruled%20the%20case%20could%20proceed.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699854480000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2020-02%2F91n9mif_sanjay-shah-denmark-twitter_625x300_04_February_20.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Ftwist-in-europes-biggest-tax-fraud-case-involving-indian-origin-tycoon-4569614%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20practice%20was%20named%20after%20Latin%20term%2C%20and%20allows%20multiple%20people%20to%20claim%20ownership%20of%20a%20stock%20and%20claim%20refunds%20on%20dividend%20tax%20that%20was%20only%20paid%20once.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Ftwist-in-europes-biggest-tax-fraud-case-involving-indian-origin-tycoon-4569614%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Ftwist