ia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fmalaika-arora-celebrates-diwali-with-family-arjun-kapoor-gives-it-a-miss-due-to-this-reason%2Farticleshow%2F105177488.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Supreme%20Court%20Circulates%20Interim%20Guidelines%20for%20Seizure%20of%20Devices%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F02102630%2F1156px-Supreme_Court_of_India_01.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%20%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3EFive%20renowned%20academics%2C%20Ram%20Ramaswamy%2C%20Madhava%20Prasad%2C%20Sujata%20Patel%2C%20Deepak%20Malghan%20and%20Mukul%20Kesavan%20petitioned%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20in%202021%20to%20regulate%20the%20search%20of%20electronic%20devices%20by%20agents%20of%20the%20state%2C%20usually%20the%20police.%20In%20the%20course%20of%20hearings%2C%20these%20petitioners%20have%20suggested%20a%20set%20of%20guidelines%20to%20be%20issued%20as%20directions%20by%20the%20court.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20November%209%2C%202023%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20directed%20that%20the%20suggested%20guidelines%20be%20circulated%20to%20the%20Union%20government%20and%20the%20states.%20In%20fact%2C%20two%20days%20earlier%2C%20on%20November%207%2C%20while%20hearing%20a%20petition%20by%20the%20Foundation%20for%20Media%20Professionals%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20had%20asked%20the%20Union%20to%20frame%20guidelines%20on%20this%20point%2C%20and%20remarked%20that%20uncontrolled%20power%20to%20access%20devices%20of%20journalists%20was%20unacceptable.%20The%20union%20government%20is%20expected%20to%20take%20into%20account%20the%20circulated%20draft%20of%20guidelines%20and%20submit%20a%20response%20in%20court.%20This%20is%20a%20big%20leap%20in%20establishing%20procedures%20around%20what%20has%20been%20arbitrary%20so%20far.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3E%E2%80%9CAn%20entire%20life%2C%20an%20entire%20profession%20and%20much%20more%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20her%20synopsis%20of%20arguments%20introducing%20the%20suggested%20guidelines%2C%20senior%20counsel%20Nitya%20Ramakrishnan%20said%20that%20Indian%20law%20on%20search%20and%20seizure%2C%20as%20it%20stands%2C%20is%20observed%20more%20in%20the%20breach%20and%20fails%20to%20comprehend%20the%20sheer%20breadth%20of%20information%20that%20would%20be%20present%20in%20any%20one%20electronic%20device.%20Provisions%20for%20the%20search%20or%20production%20of%20a%20%E2%80%98thing%E2%80%99%20or%20%E2%80%98%20document%E2%80%99%20will%20not%20do%20for%20electronic%20devices%2C%20which%20are%20not%20any%20one%20document%20or%20thing%2C%20but%20%E2%80%9C%20an%20entire%20life%2C%20an%20entire%20profession%20and%20much%20more%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fdevice-seizures-making-a-mockery-of-landmark-privacy-ruling%5C%22%3EDevice%20Seizures%20Are%20Making%20a%20Mockery%20of%20The%20Supreme%20Court%E2%80%99s%20Landmark%20Privacy%20Ruling%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20landmark%202017%20Puttaswamy%20judgement%20recognises%20that%20privacy%20is%20a%20fundamental%20right%20that%20is%20entitled%20to%20a%20special%20protection%20in%20this%20digital%20age%2C%20and%20a%20regimen%20as%20followed%20in%20other%20democratic%20jurisdictions%20is%20sorely%20required%20in%20India%2C%20where%20abuse%20of%20state%20power%20and%20intrusion%20on%20privacy%20is%20rampant.%20It%20is%20reported%20that%20devices%20of%20over%2090%20journalists%20were%20taken%20by%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20(ED)%20after%20the%20arrest%20of%20the%20%3Cem%3ENewsClick%3C%2Fem%3E%20editor%2C%20Prabir%20Purkayastha%20and%20his%20colleague%20human%20resources%20head%20Amit%20Chakraborty%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fnewsclick-founder-prabir-purkayastha-arrested-in-uapa-case%2Farticle67376922.ece%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ein%20an%20alleged%20terror%20case.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3EDevices%20of%20family%20members%20and%20whole%20establishments%20are%20taken%20away%20and%20never%20returned.%C2%A0%20Moving%20the%20court%20for%20their%20return%20takes%20at%20the%20very%20least%20a%20year%2C%20even%20when%20diligently%20pursued%2C%20she%20argued.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EGlobal%20context%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20countries%20like%20the%20UK%20and%20the%20US%2C%20all%20search%20and%20seizures%2C%20including%20those%20of%20electronic%20devices%2C%20are%20subject%20to%20the%20strictest%20of%20conditions.%20Additional%20protocols%20are%20in%20place%20for%20dealing%20with%20electronic%20devices.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20US%2C%20the%20Privacy%20Protection%20Act%20forbids%20any%20search%20or%20seizure%20of%20material%20belonging%20to%20those%20involved%20in%20First%20Amendment%20activities.%20Work%20related%20to%20freedom%20of%20expression%20such%20as%20that%20of%20journalists%2C%20creative%20artists%2C%20academics%2C%20scientific%20researchers%20is%20considered%20as%20protected%20by%20the%20First%20Amendment.%20Such%20materials%20are%20exempt%20from%20search%20as%20a%20source%20of%20evidence.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20UK%20forbids%20search%20of%20or%20access%20to%20excluded%2C%20privileged%20or%20personal%20material%2C%20except%20under%20extra%20strict%20terms%2C%20and%20only%20upon%20a%20judicial%20warrant.%20In%20any%20event%2C%20search%20without%20a%20judicial%20warrant%20is%20the%20exception%20rather%20than%20the%20rule%20in%20these%20countries%2C%20unlike%20the%20situation%20in%20India.%20The%20laws%20of%20the%20UK%20and%20the%20USA%20had%20already%20been%20placed%20before%20the%20apex%20court%20in%20a%20compilation%20submitted%20by%20the%20petitioner%20academics.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EThe%20golden%20five%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EExtensively%20footnoted%20with%20references%20to%20the%20law%20in%20these%20overseas%20jurisdictions%2C%20the%20guidelines%20suggested%20by%20the%20academics%20comprise%2018%20points%20which%20may%20be%20summarised%20in%20five%20broad%20points%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Col%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3EWhat%20exactly%20is%20sought%20from%20an%20electronic%20device%20and%20why%2C%20must%20be%20produced%20in%20writing.%20This%20specificity%20must%20be%20reflected%20in%20a%20judicial%20warrant%20and%20must%20be%20shown%20as%20a%20basis%20for%20an%20emergency%20seizure.%20Before%20effecting%20a%20seizure%2C%20this%20written%20record%20will%20be%20served%20on%20the%20owner%20of%20the%20device%20or%20the%20person%20from%20whom%20it%20is%20to%20be%20taken.%20No%20one%20shall%20be%20summoned%20to%20produce%20their%20devices%20by%20the%20police.%20Search%20authorised%20by%20a%20warrant%20must%20be%20the%20rule%20and%20an%20emergency%20search%20and%20seizure%20an%20exception%20to%20be%20justified%20in%20writing.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20device%20seized%20will%20be%20first%20examined%20by%20an%20independent%20authority%20in%20the%20presence%20of%20the%20owner%2Fagent%2C%20and%20all%20privileged%2C%20personal%20and%20professional%20material%20%E2%80%93%20in%20fact%20all%20material%20irrelevant%20to%20the%20inquiry%20will%20be%20identified%2C%20separated%2C%20protected%20and%20returned%20immediately.%20Only%20material%20directly%20relevant%20to%20the%20investigation%20shall%20be%20taken%20away%20%E2%80%93%20after%20making%20three%20copies%2C%20one%20for%20the%20owner%2C%20one%20to%20be%20left%20sealed%20with%20the%20independent%20authority%20and%20the%20third%20taken%20for%20investigation%2C%20with%20the%20hash%20value%20noted%20at%20every%20stage.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIn%20the%20rare%20event%20that%20the%20device%20needs%20to%20be%20taken%20by%20the%20investigators%2C%20it%20must%20only%20be%20after%20enabling%20removal%20of%20all%20information%20irrelevant%20to%20investigation.%20The%20date%20and%20place%20of%20its%20return%20shall%20be%20indicated%20in%20the%20memo%2C%20which%20is%20to%20be%20made%20during%20the%20search%2C%20return%20of%20the%20device%20must%20be%20within%2030%20days%20of%20the%20seizure.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ECompelled%20disclosure%20of%20passwords%20is%20forbidden%20unless%20any%20statute%20expressly%20allows%20for%20it.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ENo%20material%20seized%20in%20contravention%20of%20the%20guidelines%20shall%20be%20used%20in%20any%20court%20or%20in%20any%20manner.%20These%20conditions%20cannot%20be%20waived.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EThe%20importance%20of%20statute%20law%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20challenges%20to%20laws%20enabling%20the%20State%E2%80%99s%20access%20to%20data%20stored%20in%20electronic%20devices%2C%20notably%20Section%2069%20of%20the%20IT%20Act%2C%20and%20other%20search%20and%20seizure%20provisions%20are%20pending%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20these%20guidelines%20are%20proposed%20by%20the%20petitioners%20as%20an%20interim%20measure%20until%20they%20can%20be%20replaced%20by%20more%20permanent%20measures%20that%20may%20come%20from%20court%20directions%20or%20through%20legislation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESignificantly%2C%20many%20directions%20originally%20issued%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20have%20later%20been%20reproduced%20in%20statute%20law.%20For%20example%2C%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fncwapps.nic.in%2FpdfReports%2FSexual%2520Harassment%2520at%2520Workplace%2520(English).pdf%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EVishakha%20guidelines%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20led%20to%20the%20Prevention%20of%20Sexual%20Harassment%20at%20the%20Workplace%20Act%20(what%20we%20know%20as%20POSH%20now)%20and%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.humanrightsinitiative.org%2Fdownload%2F1589358673DK%2520Basu%2520guidelines%2520English.pdf%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EDK%20Basu%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3Eand%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findiankanoon.org%2Fdoc%2F2982624%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EArunesh%20Kumar%20guidelines%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20led%20to%20amendments%20in%20the%20Code%20of%20Criminal%20Procedure%20(CrPC).%20More%20recently%20in%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findiankanoon.org%2Fdoc%2F7148380%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ESatender%20Kumar%20Antil%20vs%20Central%20Bureau%20Of%20Investigation%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3Eon%2011%20July%2C%202022%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20given%20extensive%20directions%20for%20the%20bail%20of%20those%20in%20custody%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699853582000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F02102630%2F1156px-Supreme_Court_of_India_01.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fsupreme-court-circulates-interim-guidelines-for-seizure-of-devices%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Of%20late%2C%20the%20unauthorised%20and%20arbitrary%20seizure%20of%20devices%20by%20police%20from%20journalists%2C%20academics%20and%20lawyers%20have%20led%20to%20outrage%20about%20the%20rising%20impunity%20and%20absence%20of%20rules%20around%20it.%20The%20apex%20court%E2%80%99s%20guidelines%20should%20go%20some%20distance%20to%20set%20up%20guardrails.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fsupreme-court-circulates-interim-guidelines-for-seizure-of-devices%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Woman%20employed%20at%20Agra%20hotel%20gang-raped%2C%205%20arrested%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699853465000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-105175644%2Cimgsize-23156.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fagra%2Fwoman-employed-at-agra-hotel-gang-raped-five-arre