t%2C%20according%20to%20Israeli%20news%20and%20entertainment%20website%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mako.co.il%2Fnews-law%2F2023_q4%2FArticle-a923bd7d8f8bb81026.htm%5C%22%3EMako.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20teacher%2C%20who%20has%20not%20been%20named%2C%C2%A0has%20previously%20called%20Israeli%20soldiers%20''child%20killers''%20in%20a%20social%20media%20post.%C2%A0Earlier%20in%20the%20year%2C%20he%20wrote%20that%20someone%20who%20carried%20out%20a%20car-ramming%20attack%20''was%20not%20a%20terrorist%2C''%20and%20also%20encouraged%20attacks%20on%20soldiers%20and%20police%20officers.%20Further%2C%20he%20urged%C2%A0high%20school%20students%20to%20refuse%20to%20serve%20in%20the%20army.%C2%A0%20''They%20know%20well%20what%20the%20results%20will%20be%2C%20and%20still%2C%20they%20chose%20to%20obey%2C''%20he%20wrote%20of%20the%20pilots.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20appeared%20before%20a%20court%20on%20Friday%2C%20where%20judges%20extended%20his%20custody%20at%20least%20until%20Monday%2C%20while%20police%20continue%20their%20investigation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0Israeli%20police%20have%20so%20far%20recorded%2048%20indictments%20of%20this%20crime%20and%20are%20investigating%20381%20publications%20over%20statements%20made%20regarding%20the%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699852320000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Fnl1tpci8_israel-hamas-attack-_625x300_13_November_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisraeli-history-teacher-arrested-for-justifying-atrocities-committed-by-hamas-4569513%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20teacher%20wrote%20several%20messages%20on%20WhatsApp%20wherein%20he%20asserted%20Hamas%20was%20free%20to%20do%20everything%20in%20its%20power%20to%20fight%20back%20against%20Israel.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A18%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisraeli-history-teacher-arrested-for-justifying-atrocities-