-cities-in-worlds-10-most-polluted-list-after-diwali-4569491%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fdelhi-news%2Fdelhi-pollution-delhi-air-pollution-diwali-pollution-cracker-delhi-among-3-indian-cities-in-worlds-10-most-polluted-list-after-diwali-4569491%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Netanyahu%20Hints%20At%20Possible%20Deal%20To%20Free%20Hostages%20Amid%20Ceasefire%20Calls%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIsraeli%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%20told%20US%20media%20Sunday%20a%20deal%20could%20be%20afoot%20to%20free%20hostages%20held%20by%20Hamas%20in%20Gaza%2C%20but%20declined%20to%20provide%20details%20for%20fear%20of%20scuttling%20the%20potential%20plan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20heard%20that%20there%20was%20an%20impending%20deal%20of%20this%20kind%20or%20of%20that%20kind%20and%20then%20we%20learned%20that%20it%20was%20all%20hokum.%20But%20the%20minute%20we%20started%20the%20ground%20operation%2C%20that%20began%20to%20change%2C%26quot%3B%20Netanyahu%20told%20NBC%20show%20%26quot%3BMeet%20the%20Press.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20whether%20there%20is%20a%20potential%20deal%20to%20free%20more%20of%20the%20hostages%20being%20held%20by%20Hamas%20militants%2C%20Netanyahu%20replied%3A%20%26quot%3BThere%20could%20be.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20leader%20stopped%20short%20of%20providing%20specifics%20about%20any%20plan%20that%20might%20be%20coming%20together%20to%20free%20some%20or%20all%20of%20the%20239%20hostages%20that%20Israel%20says%20are%20being%20held%20captive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20the%20less%20I%20say%20about%20it%2C%20the%20more%20I'll%20increase%20the%20chances%20that%20it%20materializes%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENetanyahu%20has%20flatly%20rejected%20calls%20for%20a%20ceasefire%20in%20Gaza%20without%20release%20of%20the%20hostages.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20series%20of%20appearances%20on%20US%20Sunday%20talk%20shows%2C%20he%20sought%20to%20make%20clear%20Israel%20was%20doing%20everything%20it%20can%20to%20rescue%20or%20secure%20release%20of%20those%20held%20captive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20on%20CNN%20whether%20he%20agrees%20with%20the%20US%20position%20that%20an%20extended%20pause%20in%20Gaza%20fighting%20is%20needed%20in%20order%20to%20get%20the%20hostages%20released%20safely%2C%20Netanyahu%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BWe%20don't%20disagree%20with%20that.%20We%20need%20to%20get%20our%20hostages%20out.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20Palestinian%20official%20in%20Gaza%2C%20however%2C%20laid%20the%20blame%20for%20inaction%20at%20Netanyahu's%20feet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNetanyahu%20is%20responsible%20for%20the%20delay%20and%20obstacles%20in%20reaching%20a%20preliminary%20agreement%20on%20the%20release%20of%20several%20prisoners%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20official%20told%20AFP%20on%20condition%20of%20anonymity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20is%20not%20interested%20in%20finding%20them%20alive%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20source%20said.%20%26quot%3BHe%20is%20only%20concerned%20with%20preserving%20his%20political%20future.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhite%20House%20National%20Security%20Council%20spokesman%20John%20Kirby%20told%20MSNBC%20that%20there%20has%20been%20%26quot%3Bactive%20negotiation%20and%20conversations%20going%20on%20with%20our%20counterparts%20in%20the%20region%26quot%3B%20on%20a%20potential%20hostages%20deal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20like%20Netanyahu%2C%20he%20stayed%20quiet%20on%20details.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20less%20said%20publicly%20about%20these%20sensitive%20negotiations%20and%20conversations%2C%20probably%20the%20better%2C%26quot%3B%20Kirby%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Netanyahu%20also%20addressed%20the%20issue%20of%20Gaza's%20hospitals%2C%20which%20have%20become%20trapped%20in%20the%20fighting%2C%20and%20in%20particular%20Al-Shifa%2C%20the%20Hamas-run%20territory's%20largest%20hospital%2C%20which%20authorities%20say%20faces%20a%20catastrophic%20situation.%3C%