ginning%E2%80%99%20Review%3A%20Netflix%20Doc%20Goes%20Back%20in%20Time%20to%20Explore%20the%20Origins%20of%20Anti-Blackness%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699849800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FStamped-From-the-Beginning.jpg%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D563%26crop%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1235788950%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Many%20of%20us%20probably%20think%20we%20know%20how%20racist%20anti-Black%20ideas%20started%20or%20think%20racism%20was%20always%20part%20of%20the%20human%20condition.%20Director%20Roger%20Ross%20Williams%20challenges%20these%20notions%20with%20his%20adaptation%20of%20Ibram%20X.%20Kendi%E2%80%99s%20book%20%E2%80%9CStamped%20From%20the%20Beginning.%E2%80%9D%20Relying%20on%20testimony%20from%20Black%20female%20scholars%20and%20Kendi%E2%80%99s%20research%2C%20the%20helmer%20(whose%20previous%20%5B%E2%80%A6%5D%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Peter%20Debruge%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2023%2Ffilm%2Freviews%2Fstamped-from-the-beginning-review-ibram-x-kendi-1235788950%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fvariety.com%2F2023%2Ffilm%2Freviews%2Fstamped-from-the-beginning-review-ibram-x-kendi-1235788950%2Famp%2F%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2023%2Ffilm%2Freviews%2Fstamped-from-the-beginning-review-ibram-x-kendi-1235788950%2Famp%2F%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Adani%20Group%20Plots%20Expansion%20Of%20Overseas%20Port%20Empire%20After%20US%20Funding%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EStanding%20before%20Sri%20Lankan%20officials%20and%20US%20diplomats%20in%20Colombo%20hotel%20last%20week%2C%20Karan%20Adani%20said%20that%20a%20newly%20inked%20%24553%20million%20US%20government%20financing%20deal%20toward%20a%20port%20terminal%20being%20developed%20by%20his%20family's%20conglomerate%20was%20a%20%26quot%3Breaffirmation%20by%20the%20international%20community.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20announcement%20marked%20a%20welcome%20reprieve%20for%20Adani%20Group%20following%20a%20damaging%20short-seller%20attack%20and%20a%20number%20of%20corporate%20fraud%20allegations%20leveled%20against%20it%20this%20year.%20It%20also%20signaled%20Washington's%20endorsement%20for%20the%20port%20empire%20owned%20by%20Karan's%20father%20and%20billionaire%20Gautam%20Adani%20that%20would%20help%20curb%20China's%20maritime%20influence%20in%20the%20Indian%20ocean.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThose%20waters%20account%20for%20more%20than%20one-third%20of%20the%20world's%20bulk%20cargo%20traffic%20and%20two-thirds%20of%20oil%20shipments.%20Chakri%20Lokapriya%2C%20chief%20investment%20officer%20at%20TCG%20Asset%20Management%20Co.%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20called%20Adani's%20port%20ambitions%20a%20%26quot%3Bstrategic%26quot%3B%20play%2C%20assisting%20India%20to%20counter%20China's%20own%20string%20of%20ports%20in%20its%20backyard%2C%20stretching%20from%20Sri%20Lanka%20to%20Pakistan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%20Adani%20Ports%20and%20Special%20Economic%20Zone%20Ltd.%2C%20seen%20as%20the%20conglomerate's%20crown%20jewel%2C%20is%20eyeing%20further%20%26quot%3Bopportunities%20in%20our%20neighboring%20countries%2C%26quot%3B%20Karan%20Adani%2C%20the%20operator's%20chief%20executive%20officer%2C%20told%20Bloomberg%20News%20in%20the%20Sri%20Lankan%20capital.%20Those%20include%20potential%20ventures%20in%20Bangladesh%2C%20as%20well%20as%20East%20African%20and%20Southeast%20Asian%20nations%2C%20including%20Tanzania%20and%20Vietnam%2C%20adding%20to%20its%20existing%20Sri%20Lanka%20and%20Israel%20developments%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20world%20that's%20%26quot%3Blooking%20beyond%20China%20-%20it%20is%20indeed%20a%20Chinese-styled%20expansion%20by%20Adani%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Sanjiv%20Bhasin%2C%20director%20at%20Mumbai-based%20IIFL%20Securities%20Ltd.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Long%20Game'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20funding%20for%20the%20Adani-led%20West%20Container%20Terminal%20in%20Colombo%20via%20the%20Intentional%20Development%20Finance%20Corp.%20was%20a%20shot-in-the-arm%20after%20a%20torrid%20few%20years%20for%20the%20Adani%20Group's%20overseas%20expansion%20efforts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20conglomerate%20pulled%20the%20plug%20on%20its%20plans%20to%20build%20a%20port%20in%20Myanmar%20following%20a%20military%20coup.%20Last%20year%2C%20Adani%20faced%20protests%20and%20political%20criticism%20in%20Sri%20Lanka%2C%20which%20characterized%20the%20firm's%20port%20and%20energy%20proposals%20as%20opaque%20projects%20pushed%20onto%20the%20country%20by%20New%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20while%20Adani%20Ports%20is%20India's%20largest%20operator%20-%20with%20a%20collection%20of%2014%20domestic%20terminals%20that%20can%20handle%20600%20million%20metric%20tons%20of%20capacity%20-%20it%20remains%20a%20relative%20minnow%20overseas.%20It'll%20need%20to%20scale%20up%20manifold%20before%20challenging%20China's%20wide%20sphere%20of%20influence%2C%20which%20is%20built%20on%20investments%20in%20more%20than%2090%20ports%20outside%20its%20borders%2C%2013%20of%20which%20have%20majority%20Chinese%20ownership%2C%20according%20to%20the%20US%20Council%20on%20Foreign%20Relations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGiven%20that%20Beijing%20is%20so%20far%20out%20front%2C%20it's%20hard%20for%20Adani%20or%20anyone%20else%20to%20hold%20a%20candle%20to%20China's%20infrastructure%20investments%20anytime%20in%20the%20foreseeable%20future%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Michael%20Kugelman%2C%20director%20of%20the%20South%20Asia%20Institute%20at%20the%20Wilson%20Center%20in%20Washington.%20%26quot%3BBut%20Adani%20and%20his%20companies%20are%20playing%20a%20long%20game.%20They're%20looking%20to%20slowly%20but%20consistently%20build%20out%20new%20investments%20in%20South%20Asia%20and%20beyond.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIndia%20Focus%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGautam%20Adani%20has%20openly%20criticised%20China%20in%20the%20past.%C2%A0Adani%20Ports'%20domestic%20business%20accounts%20for%20about%2090%25%20of%20the%20firm's%20revenues%2C%20Karan%20Adani%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20%26quot%3Bthis%20will%20remain%20as%20we%20are%20expanding%20in%20India.%26quot%3B%20A%20new%20Adani%20transshipment%20terminal%20in%20the%20southern%20state%20of%20Kerala%20was%20inaugurated%20last%20month%2C%20aiming%20to%20grab%20a%20bigger%20slice%20of%20international%20cargo.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTrade%20is%20booming%2C%20we%20are%20just%20doing%20a%20catch%20up%20game%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20always%20short%20of%20capacity%20and%20that%20is%20hurting%20Indian%20trade.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20comments%20follow%20PM%20Modi's%20outline%20in%20September%20for%20an%20Indian-Middle%20East-Europe%20Economic%20Corridor%2C%20part%20of%20which%20may%20run%20through%20Adani's%20port%20in%20Israel's%20Haifa.%20They%20also%20hint%20that%20the%20group%20is%20looking%20to%20head%20into%20a%20new%20expansionary%20phrase%20after%20paring%20back%20some%20plans%20to%20reassure%20investors%20following%20Hindenburg%20Research's%20January%20broadside.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20US%20government%20loan%20package%20and%20recent%20investment%20from%20the%20likes%20of%20TotalEnergies%20SE%20in%20Adani's%20green%20energy%20business%2C%20it's%20premature%20to%20say%20%26quot%3Bthe%20floodgates%20of%20international%20finance%20will%20open%20for%20the%20Adani%20Group%26quot%3B%20as%20increased%20scrutiny%20on%20the%20conglomerate's%20business%20practices%20remain%2C%20said%20Samantha%20Custer%2C%20director%20of%20policy%20analysis%20at%20AidData%20at%20William%20%26amp%3B%20Mary's%20Global%20Research%20Institute.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20August%2C%20Adani%20Port's%20auditor%20Deloitte%20Haskins%20%26amp%3B%20Sells%20LLP%20resigned%20after%20it%20couldn't%20determine%20if%20the%20business%20was%20fully%20compliant%20with%20local%20laws%2C%20flagging%20concerns%20over%20transactions%20between%20Adani%20Ports%20and%20three%20entities%20that%20Adani%20said%20were%20unrelated%20parties.%20The%20reasons%20for%20Deloitte's%20resignation%20%26quot%3Bwere%20not%20convincing%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20chairman%20of%20the%20company's%20audit%20committee%20said%20at%20the%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20global%20markets%20and%20financing%20conditions%20remaining%20tight%2C%20Adani%20Ports%20may%20also%20%26quot%3Bface%20the%20challenge%20of%20raising%20funds%20to%20fuel%20expansion%20as%20the%20cost%20of%20the%20debt%20is%20going%20to%20be%20high%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Bhasin%20at%20IIFL%20Securities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Reputational%20Risks'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShares%20in%20Adani%20Ports%20fell%201.5%25%20on%20Thursday%20after%20it%20posted%20a%204%25%20year-on-year%20rise%20in%20quarterly%20net%20income%20to%2017.48%20billion%20rupees%20(%24210%20million)%2C%20missing%20average%20analyst%20estimates.%20But%20the%20firm's%20%26quot%3Bresilient%20growth%20capability%20is%20visible%20if%20a%204.55%20billion-rupee%20accounting%20write-off%20from%20the%20adoption%20of%20a%20new%20tax%20regime%20is%20discarded%2C%26quot%3B%20Denise%20Wong%2C%20an%20analyst%20at%20Blomberg%20Intelligence%2C%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESanford%20C.%20Bernstein%20analysts%20Nikhil%20Nigania%20and%20Anusha%20Madireddy%20in%20a%20report%20published%20on%20Friday%20also%20pointed%20to%20%26quot%3Bstrong%26quot%3B%20quarterly%20volume%20growth%20up%2017%25%20from%20the%20same%20quarter%20last%20year%2C%20with%20gross%20debt%20falling%20to%20472%20billion%20rupees%20from%20498%20billion%20rupees%20at%20the%20end%20of%20March.%20They%20said%20that%20actions%20taken%20to%20curb%20leverage%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20Hindenburg's%20attack%20%26quot%3Bcould%20be%20a%20blessing%20in%20disguise.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAdani's%20businesses%20have%20proved%20to%20be%20quite%20resilient%20in%20the%20face%20of%20the%20fraud%20allegations%2C%