20toward%20pro-Palestinian%20protesters%20was%20blamed%20for%20drawing%20out%20far-right%20groups%20that%20clashed%20with%20officers%20during%20mass%20demonstrations%20in%20the%20capital%20Saturday.%20On%20Sunday%2C%20a%20Downing%20Street%20official%20declined%20to%20say%20if%20Braverman%20would%20still%20be%20in%20her%20job%20in%20a%20week%2C%20while%20Defense%20Secretary%20Grant%20Shapps%20responded%20to%20the%20same%20question%20only%20by%20noting%20that%20%26quot%3Ba%20week%20is%20a%20long%20time%20in%20politics.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERishi%20Sunak%20has%20come%20under%20pressure%20to%20punish%20Braverman%20for%20criticizing%20the%20Metropolitan%20Police%20in%20a%20newspaper%20commentary%20hours%20after%20he%20had%20appeared%20to%20resolve%20disputes%20with%20the%20force's%20commissioner%20about%20protests%20overlapping%20with%20annual%20events%20to%20commemorate%20Britain's%20war%20dead.%20Two%20Cabinet%20members%20on%20Sunday%20described%20the%20challenge%20to%20the%20prime%20minister's%20authority%20as%20untenable%2C%20despite%20Braverman's%20strong%20popularity%20among%20the%20Conservative%20Party's%20right%20wing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20Sunak%20keeps%20Braverman%2C%20he'll%20feed%20efforts%20by%20Labour%20leader%20Keir%20Starmer%20to%20paint%20him%20as%20weak%20ahead%20of%20an%20expected%20general%20election%20next%20year%2C%20one%20Tory%20lawmaker%20said.%20Ousting%20her%20may%20prompt%20theright%20to%20revolt%2C%20leaving%20the%20Conservatives%20even%20more%20divided%2C%20another%20said%2C%20calling%20it%20a%20lose-lose%20situation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMore%20than%20300%2C000%20pro-Palestine%20demonstrators%20turned%20out%20Saturday%20for%20the%20largest%20march%20in%20London%20since%20the%20start%20of%20the%20Israel-Hamas%20conflict%20more%20than%20a%20month%20ago.%20Some%20protest%20leaders%20credited%20Braverman%20-%20who%20had%20branded%20participants%20as%20%26quot%3Bhate%20marchers%2C%26quot%3B%20in%20reference%20to%20reports%20that%20past%20events%20had%20included%20chants%20of%20%26quot%3Bjihad%26quot%3B%20-%20with%20increasing%20public%20support.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Met%20has%20also%20blamed%20the%20political%20drama%20for%20making%20their%20efforts%20to%20maintain%20public%20order%20more%20difficult.%20The%20conflict%20in%20Gaza%2C%20the%20Armistice%20Day%20holiday%20and%20the%20intense%20debate%20about%20protest%20and%20policing%20%26quot%3Ball%20combined%20to%20increase%20community%20tensions%2C%26quot%3B%20Assistant%20Police%20Commissioner%20Matt%20Twist%20said%20late%20Saturday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShapps%2C%20who%20was%20representing%20the%20government%20on%20the%20Sunday%20political%20talk%20shows%2C%20deflected%20questions%20about%20Braverman's%20responsibility%2C%20telling%20Sky%20News%3A%20%26quot%3BThese%20marches%20were%20already%20going%20to%20happen.%20These%20counter-protests%20were%20already%20going%20to%20happen.%26quot%3B%20When%20asked%20about%20her%20future%2C%20he%20said%20the%20makeup%20of%20the%20government%20was%20a%20matter%20for%20the%20prime%20minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%20made%20some%20145%20arrests%20during%20the%20demonstrations%20Saturday%2C%20including%20scores%20of%20counter-protesters%20whom%20police%20prevented%20from%20intercepting%20the%20largely%20peaceful%20pro-Palestine%20march.%20The%20Met%20said%20Sunday%20that%20seven%20men%20had%20been%20charged%20with%20a%20variety%20of%20offenses%2C%20including%20assault%20on%20an%20emergency%20worker%2C%20criminal%20damage%20and%20possession%20of%20an%20offensive%20weapon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20can't%20go%20on%2C%26quot%3B%20Braverman%20said%20on%20the%20social%20media%20platform%20X%20on%20Sunday%2C%20thanking%20police%20and%20calling%20the%20injuries%20suffered%20by%20some%20officers%20%26quot%3Ban%20outrage.%26quot%3B%20While%20she%20mentioned%20%26quot%3Bviolence%20and%20aggression%26quot%3B%20by%20members%20of%20both%20camps%2C%20she%20focused%20her%20criticism%20on%20the%20pro-Palestine%20marchers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAntisemitism%20and%20other%20forms%20of%20racism%20together%20with%20the%20valorising%20of%20terrorism%20on%20such%20a%20scale%20is%20deeply%20troubling%2C%26quot%3B%20Braverman%20said%20on%20the%20platform%20formerly%20known%20as%20Twitter.%20Police%20have%20posted%20photographs%20on%20social%20media%20of%20people%20they%20are%20looking%20to%20identify%20over%20possible%20anti-Semitic%20hate%20crimes%20and%20supporting%20Hamas%2C%20which%20the%20UK%20has%20designated%20as%20a%20terrorist%20organization.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBraverman%2C%20who%20oversees%20immigration%20policy%2C%20is%20closely%20linked%20to%20another%20looming%20milestone%20for%20Sunak%3A%20a%20UK%20Supreme%20Court%20ruling%20due%20Wednesday%20on%20the%20legality%20of%20the%20government's%20plan%20to%20deport%20asylum-seekers%20to%20Rwanda.%20The%20timing%20complicates%20the%20prime%20minister's%20decision%20on%20Braverman%20because%20waiting%20until%20after%20the%20judgment%20is%20handed%20down%20risks%20making%20it%20look%20like%20the%20two%20events%20were%20related.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20isn't%20confident%20it%20will%20win%20the%20Rwanda%20case%2C%20the%20Downing%20Street%20official%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20Conservative%20officials%20were%20bracing%20for%20a%20Cabinet%20shake-up%2C%20which%20they%20believed%20could%20come%20as%20soon%20as%20Monday%2C%20when%20Sunak's%20public%20schedule%20is%20clear%20other%20than%20a%20foreign%20policy%20speech%20in%20the%20evening.%20Deputy%20Prime%20Minister%20Oliver%20Dowden%20held%20meetings%20last%20week%20to%20discuss%20a%20potential%20reshuffle%2C%20Bloomberg%20reported%20last%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20Tory%20lawmakers%20have%20privately%20urged%20Sunak%20to%20sack%20Braverman%2C%20echoing%20public%20demands%20for%20her%20exit%20by%20the%20opposition%20Labour%20Party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShe%20inflamed%20tension%2C%20she%20also%20attacked%20the%20police%2C%20undermined%20respect%20for%20the%20police%20at%20a%20really%20important%20time%20-%20that%20was%20highly%20irresponsible%2C%26quot%3B%20Yvette%20Cooper%2C%20Labour's%20shadow%20home%20secretary%2C%20told%20the%20BBC%20on%20Sunday.%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20just%20not%20the%20way%20any%20home%20secretary%20would%20do%20that%20job%20other%20than%20Suella%20Braverman%2C%20and%20Rishi%20Sunak%20is%20being%20so%20weak%20that%20he%20is%20allowing%20her%20to%20do%20that.%20It%20is%20very%20damaging.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699845360000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-10%2Ftv8vjs68_rishi-sunak-suella-braverman-afp-pic_625x300_27_October_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Frishi-sunak-suella-braverman-rishi-sunak-faces-big-sacking-decision-in-most-challenging-week-as-uk-pm-4569389%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20immediate%20threat%20of%20chaos%20in%20London's%20streets%20has%20subsided%2C%20but%20that%20may%20only%20provide%20a%20brief%20respite%20for%20Rishi%20Sunak%20as%20he%20enters%20one%20of%20his%20most%20consequential%20weeks%20as%20Britain's%20prime%20minister.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Frishi-sunak-suella-braverman-rishi-sunak-faces-big-sacking-decision-in-most-challenging-week-as-uk-pm-4569389%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Frishi-sunak-suella-braverman-rishi-sunak-faces-big-sacking-decision-in-most-challenging-week-as-uk-pm-4569389%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Frishi-sunak-suella-braverman-rishi-sunak-faces-big-sacking-decision-in-most-challenging-week-as-uk-pm-4569389%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Boeing%20in%20final%20leg%20of%20major%20deal%20with%20Emirates%20for%20its%20wide%20body%20777x%20jets%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699844877000%2C%22visual%2