lican-presidential-candidate-tim-scott-announces-he-is-dropping-out-of-the-2024-race%2Farticleshow%2F105174107.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm-timesofindia-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Frepublican-presidential-candidate-tim-scott-announces-he-is-dropping-out-of-the-2024-race%2Famp_articleshow%2F105174107.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Frepublican-presidential-candidate-tim-scott-announces-he-is-dropping-out-of-the-2024-race%2Famp_articleshow%2F105174107.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22US%20Faces%20Shutdown%20Risk%20Despite%20New%20Compromise%20Plan%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20still%20faces%20a%20risk%20of%20a%20government%20shutdown%20at%20the%20end%20of%20this%20week%20despite%20a%20new%20compromise%20plan%20by%20Speaker%20Mike%20Johnson%20that%20leaves%20out%20hardline%20conservative%20priorities%20like%20cutting%20spending%20and%20curtailing%20migration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20shutdown%20would%20threaten%20a%20downward%20US%20credit%20rating%20adjustment%20by%20Moody's%20Investors%20Service%2C%20which%20has%20cited%20political%20dysfunction%20as%20a%20growing%20risk%20to%20bond%20investors.%20A%20federal%20funding%20lapse%20would%20also%20have%20political%20repercussions%20for%20both%20parties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress%20has%20just%20days%20to%20pass%20a%20new%20stopgap%20bill%20before%20funding%20runs%20out%20after%20Nov.%2017.%20Johnson%20on%20Sunday%20suggested%20his%20plan%20would%20buy%20lawmakers%20time%20to%20negotiate%20individual%20spending%20bills%2C%20which%20fiscal%20conservatives%20have%20demanded.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWashington's%20spending%20addiction%20cannot%20be%20broken%20overnight%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20on%20the%20social%20media%20site%20X.%20%26quot%3BBut%20I%20will%20not%20allow%20end%20of%20year%20megabus%20spending%20packages%20to%20continue%20under%20my%20leadership.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJohnson's%20plan%20could%20still%20run%20aground%20in%20the%20face%20of%20combined%20resistance%20from%20GOP%20conservatives%20and%20the%20White%20House%2C%20which%20is%20irked%20by%20the%20lack%20of%20Ukraine%20aid%20in%20the%20plan%20and%20the%20fact%20it%20extends%20funding%20for%20some%20agencies%20to%20Jan.%2019%20and%20others%20to%20Feb.%202.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20House%20plans%20to%20vote%20on%20the%20plan%20on%20Tuesday.%20Johnson%20will%20need%20some%20Democratic%20votes%20given%20his%20narrow%20majority%20and%20opposition%20by%20fiscal%20conservatives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20before%20that%20stopgap%20vote%2C%20conservatives%20could%20block%20the%20plan%20before%20it%20comes%20to%20the%20floor%20or%20on%20a%20procedural%20vote%20setting%20up%20debate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDisappointing%20is%20as%20polite%20as%20I%20can%20muster.%20I%20will%20be%20voting%20NO%2C%26quot%3B%20conservative%20Warren%20Davidson%20of%20Ohio%20said%20on%20X%20Saturday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDemocrats%20have%20been%20muted%20in%20their%20reaction%20to%20Johnson's%20plan%20but%20there%20were%20some%20early%20signs%20it%20could%20receive%20bipartisan%20backing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20like%20what%20the%20House%20is%20talking%20about%20but%20I'm%20willing%20to%20listen%2C%26quot%3B%20Connecticut%20Senator%20Chris%20Murphy%20said%20on%20NBC's%20Meet%20the%20Press.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20White%20House%2C%20however%2C%20said%20Johnson's%20plan%20would%20only%20lead%20to%20future%20shutdowns.%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20could%20issue%20a%20formal%20veto%20threat%20later%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20bill%20lacks%20the%20strings%20that%20many%20Democrats%20had%20feared%2C%20and%20a%20veto%20threat%20could%20allow%20Republicans%20to%20blame%20the%20shutdown%20on%20the%20president.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EPolitical%20Dysfunction%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20year%20has%20brought%20the%20US%20near%20a%20debt%20default%2C%20provoked%20Fitch%20Ratings%20to%20downgrade%20the%20nation's%20sovereign%20debt%20and%20cost%20Johnson's%20predecessor%20his%20job.%20Republican%20hardliners%20ousted%20then-Speaker%20Kevin%20McCarthy%20after%20he%20offered%20a%20similar%20strings-free%20stopgap.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoody's%2C%20the%20only%20major%20credit%20grader%20still%20to%20give%20the%20US%20its%20top%20rating%2C%20on%20Friday%20changed%20its%20ratings%20outlook%20for%20the%20US%20from%20stable%20to%20negative%2C%20citing%20risks%20to%20the%20nation's%20fiscal%20strength%20and%20political%20polarization%20in%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20chaotic%20three-week%20process%20to%20elect%20a%20new%20speaker%20damaged%20Republicans'%20standing%20in%20swing%20states%2C%20according%20to%20a%20Bloomberg%20News%2FMorning%20Consult%20poll%20from%20October%2030%20through%20November%207.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20a%209%20percentage-point%20margin%2C%20swing-state%20voters%20said%20the%20speaker%20chaos%20made%20them%20more%20likely%20to%20vote%20Democratic%20in%202024%20over%20those%20who%20said%20the%20process%20made%20it%20more%20likely%20they%20would%20vote%20Republican.%20Among%20independents%2C%20the%20margin%20was%207%20points%20in%20favor%20of%20Democrats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20shutdown%20beginning%20Saturday%20would%20furlough%20hundreds%20of%20thousands%20of%20federal%20workers%20just%20before%20the%20Thanksgiving%20holiday%20and%20delay%20government%20contracts%20and%20vendor%20payments.%20Military%20personnel%2C%20law%20enforcement%20officers%20and%20other%20essential%20employees%20would%20continue%20to%20work%20but%20go%20without%20pay%20until%20the%20impasse%20is%20resolved.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFinancial%20markets%20so%20far%20have%20shrugged%20off%20the%20growing%20risk%20of%20a%20shutdown%20as%20investors%20focus%20on%20high%20interest%20rates%2C%20volatility%20in%20bond%20markets%2C%20slowing%20consumer%20spending%20and%20war%20in%20the%20Middle%20East.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20government%20shutdown%20would%20initially%20have%20a%20mild%20economic%20impact%20but%20build%20incrementally%20as%20millions%20of%20workers%20go%20without%20salary%2C%20private%20contractors%20aren't%20paid%20and%20consumer%20uncertainty%20grows.%20The%20University%20of%20Michigan%20Consumer%20Sentiment%20index%20slid%20to%20a%20six-month%20low%20in%20its%20preliminary%20November%20reading.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJohnson's%20plan%20would%20extend%20current%20funding%20until%20Jan.%2019%20for%20the%20departments%20of%20Veterans%20Affairs%2C%20Energy%2C%20Agriculture%2C%20Transportation%20as%20well%20as%20Housing%20and%20Urban%20Development%2C%20with%20the%20rest%20extended%20to%20Feb.%202.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20Senate%2C%20Republicans%20could%20move%20as%20soon%20as%20Monday%20night%20to%20block%20Democrats%20from%20starting%20work%20on%20their%20rival%20plan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenate%20Majority%20Leader%20Chuck%20Schumer%20of%20New%20York%20has%20teed%20up%20a%20procedural%20vote%20Monday%20afternoon%20to%20advance%20placeholder%20legislation%20for%20temporary%20funding%2C%20likely%20into%20January.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenators%20in%20both%20parties%20have%20also%20been%20discussing%20a%20path%20forward%20for%20%24106%20billion%20in%20security%20funding%20Biden%20sought%20for%20Ukraine%2C%20Israel%2C%20Taiwan%20and%20the%20US%20border.%20The%20package%20has%20been%20held%20up%20by%20Republican%20demands%20for%20asylum%20and%20other%20immigration%20policy%20changes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChances%20for%20reaching%20a%20deal%20this%20week%20that%20also%20includes%20the%20emergency%20security%20assistance%20are%20dropping%20given%20the%20complexity%20of%20the%20immigration%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699844400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-05%2Fjuuf5mu_us-capitol-afp_625x300_29_May_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-faces-shutdown-risk-despite-new-compromise-plan-4569371%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20US