r%2C%20he%20explained.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBooths%20is%20believed%20to%20be%20the%20first%20UK%20supermarket%20chain%20that's%20doing%20away%20with%20self-checkout%20stations%2C%20according%20to%20the%20BBC.%20But%20it's%20one%20among%20a%20growing%20number%20of%20retailers%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwalmart-costco-kroger-facing-self-checkout-reckoning-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EWamart%20and%20Costco%20that%20are%20revising%20their%20self-checkout%20strategies%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20for%20some%20US%20retailers%2C%20issues%20like%20theft%20have%20driven%20the%20self-checkout%20reckoning.%20Walmart%20said%20in%20September%20that%20it%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwalmart-pulling-self-checkout-lanes-from-some-stores-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Escrapping%20self-checkout%20lanes%20in%20at%20least%20three%20stores%20in%20Albuquerque%2C%20New%20Mexico%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20a%20decision%20that%20came%20after%20both%20employees%20and%20customers%20complained%20about%20an%20increase%20in%20theft.%20Meanwhile%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcostco-cracking-down-on-card-sharing-at-self-checkout-2023-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3ECostco%20has%20been%20cracking%20down%20on%20unauthorized%20card-sharing%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20having%20employees%20ask%20shoppers%20to%20show%20them%20their%20membership%20cards%20and%20photos%20in%20self-checkout%20lanes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmericans%20still%20seem%20to%20say%20that%20they%20prefer%20self-checkout%20stations.%20Around%2066%25%20of%20respondents%20prefer%20a%20self-service%20kiosk%20over%20a%20checkout%20lane%20managed%20by%20a%20person%2C%20according%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.playusa.com%2Famericans-and-technology%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Esurvey%20of%201%2C000%3C%2Fu%3E%3