ather%20at%20age%2012.%20During%20the%20campaign%2C%20Duvall%20called%20out%20Cameron%20for%20his%20support%20of%20a%20highly%20restrictive%20abortion%20ban%20that%20did%20not%20include%20exceptions%20for%20rape%20or%20incest.%20The%20attorney%20general%20later%20indicated%20that%20he'd%20back%20exceptions%20%26quot%3Bif%20the%20courts%20made%20us%20change%20that%20law%2C%26quot%3B%20but%20many%20voters%20have%20been%20miffed%20by%20mainstream%20GOP%20messaging%20on%20an%20issue%20that%20can%20be%20incredibly%20nuanced%2C%20even%20among%20some%20Republican%20voters.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeshear%20effectively%20painted%20the%20state's%20near-total%20abortion%20ban%20as%20%26quot%3Bextreme%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20eyes%20of%20many%20voters.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20in%20Mississippi%2C%20the%20abortion%20debate%20was%20essentially%20neutralized%2C%20as%20both%20Reeves%20and%20Presley%20are%20anti-abortion.%20While%20Democratic%20enthusiasm%20for%20Beshear%20may%20have%20been%20amplified%20over%20his%20support%20for%20exceptions%20to%20the%20Kentucky%20law%2C%20the%20opposite%20was%20true%20of%20Presley's%20candidacy%2C%20as%20Mississippi%20Democrats%20were%20likely%20to%20cite%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmississippitoday.org%2F2023%2F09%2F28%2Fbrandon-presley-expand-medicaid-tate-reeves%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMedicaid%20expansion%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmississippitoday.org%2F2023%2F09%2F26%2Fbrandon-presley-education-teachers%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eincreased%20education%20funding%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20core%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ERunning%20up%20the%20margins%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBeshear%20made%20significant%20inroads%20in%20rural%20and%20suburban%20communities%20across%20Kentucky%2C%20but%20it%20was%20the%20state's%20population%20centers%20that%20powered%20his%20victory%20over%20Cameron.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Louisville%2C%20which%20is%20consolidated%20with%20Jefferson%20County%2C%20Beshear%20won%2070%25%20of%20th