Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20Salesforce's%20massive%20annual%20tech%20conference%20that's%20drawn%20figures%20like%20Barack%20Obama%2C%20Tim%20Cook%2C%20and%20Fleetwood%20Mac%20in%20prior%20years%20%E2%80%94%20to%20give%20meditation%20tips%20to%20conference%20guests.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBrother%20Spirit%2C%20who%20also%20goes%20by%20Brother%20Ph%C3%A1p%20Linh%2C%20appears%20to%20be%20active%20on%20social%20media.%20He%20has%20almost%203%2C000%20followers%20on%20X%2C%20where%20he%20goes%20by%20the%20handle%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fbrspirituality%3Flang%3Den%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%40brspirituality%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20describes%20himself%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bcomposer-monk%26quot%3B%20who%20values%20%26quot%3Bquestions%20over%20answers%26quot%3B%20and%20believes%20that%20%26quot%3Btea%20usually%20helps.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20he%20seems%20to%20be%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fone-planet%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Estaunch%20climate%20activist%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20He%20last%20posted%20on%20X%20on%20November%2010%2C%20writing%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20all%20need%20to%20do%20what%20we%20can%20to%20prepare%20%E2%80%94%20and%20that%20includes%20our%20hearts%26quot%3B%20in%20light%20of%20global%20warming.%20He%20also%20posted%20his%20thoughts%20on%20The%20Deluge%2C%20a%20fictional%20novel%20about%20the%20climate%20crisis%2C%20calling%20it%20%26quot%3Ba%20terrifying%20and%20brilliant%20foretelling%20of%20the%20next%20few%20years%26quot%3B%20that%20%26quot%3Bsomehow%20keeps%20our%20faith%20in%20humanity's%20potential%20for%20resilience%2C%20resistance%2C%20and%20rebellion%20alive.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20Brother%20Spirit%20entered%20monastic%20training%20at%20Plum%20Village%2C%20he%20worked%20as%20a%20composer%20and%20studied%20mathematics%20at%20Cambridge%20University%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.noblewarrior.com%2F143-brother-spirit-converting-to-monastic-life-th