0the%20university's%20initial%20lack%20of%20response%20to%20the%20attacks%2C%20saying%20it%20%26quot%3Bconveyed%20the%20implicit%20approval%20of%20a%20silent%20administration.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFollowing%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbill-ackman-harvard-release-names-students-blaming-israel-violence-hamas-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econtroversial%20letter%3C%2Fa%3E%20signed%20by%2030%20student%20groups%20that%20claimed%20Israel%20was%20%26quot%3Bentirely%20responsible%26quot%3B%20for%20the%20violence%2C%20Harvard%20President%20Claudine%20Gay%20announced%20the%20creation%20of%20an%20advisory%20group%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fview.hu.harvard.edu%2F%3Fqs%3D5899cb44550a82ed4a58f77e66280d2b1e2513ee8ac057c6db942180dd51fb03b3f1bf17aec88eaad543c7f39456498e7782eafe15dc8b336847e59fa4af97f6eda225749f9c983db2fd1a622f969224%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereaffirmed%3C%2Fa%3E%20Harvard's%20%26quot%3Bcommitment%20to%20protecting%20all%20members%20of%20our%20community%20from%20harassment%20and%20marginalization.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20HCJAA%20acknowledged%20Gay's%20efforts%20but%20outlined%20several%20steps%20that%20it%20still%20wants%20to%20see%20Harvard%20take%20on%20the%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20group%20suggests%20staff%20and%20students%20undergo%20training%20on%20antisemitism%20and%20wants%20to%20see%20plans%20created%20%26quot%3Bto%20ensure%20the%20protection%20of%20Jewish%20students%20on%20campus%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bto%20curb%20the%20dissemination%20of%20hate%20speech.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20suggested%20that%20the%20university%20adopt%20the%20International%20Holocaust%20Remembrance%20Alliance's%20definition%20of%20%26quot%3Bantisemitism.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20want%20the%20University%20to%20adopt%20a%20definition%20of%20antisemitism%20that%20treats%20speech%20calling%20for%20the%20obliteration%20of%20the%20Jewish%20state%20as%20antisemitic%20and%20speech%20that%20treats%20all%20Jews%20as%20collectively%20guilty%20for%20any%20policy%20taken%20by%20the%20Jewish%20state%20as%20antisemitic%2C%26quot%3B%20Rebecca%20Claire%20Brooks%2C%20an%20organizer%20of%20the%20HCJAA%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.foxnews.com%2Fus%2Fover-1600-jewish-alumni-demand-harvard-crack-down-antisemitism-scathing-letter%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFox%20News%20Digital%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20week%2C%20the%20Biden%20Administration%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.ed.gov%2Fabout%2Foffices%2Flist%2Focr%2Fletters%2Fcolleague-202311-discrimination-harassment-shared-ancestry.pdf%3Futm_content%3D%26utm_medium%3Demail%26utm_name%3D%26utm_source%3Dgovdelivery%26utm_term%3D%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etold%20colleges%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20they%20risk%20losing%20federal%20funding%20if%20they%20don't%20take%20steps%20to%20prevent%20antisemitism%20and%20Islamophobia.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHarvard%20University%20and%20the%20HCJAA%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20Insider's%20request%20for%20comment%2C%20which%20was%20made%20outside%20of%20normal%20working%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F1600-harvard-alumni-may-pause-donations-anti-semitism-row-2023-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699802749000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6550bd6c385143459e8bbf2b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F1600-harvard-alumni-may-pause-donations-anti-semitism-row-2023-11%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Biden%20Administration%20told%20colleges%20that%20they%20risk%20losing%20federal%20funding%20if%20they%20don't%20take%20steps%20to%20prevent%20antisemitism%20and%20Islamophobia.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22pthompson%40insider.com%20(Polly%20Thompson)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A231%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2F