0who%20have%20been%20killed%2C%20injured%20or%20are%20missing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20dead%20include%20Palestinian%20freelance%20journalists%20working%20for%20international%20news%20services%2C%20and%20others%20who%20work%20for%20local%20news%20outlets%20crucial%20for%20local%20understanding%20of%20what%E2%80%99s%20happening.%20Many%20have%20died%20in%20air%20strikes%20on%20their%20homes%2C%20some%20alongside%20their%20children%20and%20families.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Israeli%20Defence%20Forces%20insist%20they%20do%20not%20target%20journalists%2C%20but%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Frsf.org%2Fen%2Fisraelpalestine-war-41-journalists-more-one-day-killed-first-month-israel-palestine-war%5C%22%3EReporters%20Without%20Borders%3C%2Fa%3E%20says%20at%20least%20ten%20have%20been%20killed%20while%20clearly%20covering%20the%20news.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20course%2C%20the%20life%20of%20a%20journalist%20is%20worth%20no%20more%20than%20any%20other%20civilian%2C%20and%20in%20such%20a%20horrifically%20violent%20crisis%2C%20which%20has%20already%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fpressure-israel-over-civilians-steps-up-ceasefire-calls-rebuffed-2023-11-06%2F%5C%22%3Ekilled%20more%20than%2010%2C000%20people%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20it%20is%20hardly%20surprising%20some%20of%20them%20will%20be%20journalists.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20there%20is%20mounting%20evidence%20journalists%20have%20been%20targeted%2C%20harassed%2C%20beaten%20and%20threatened.%20A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcpj.org%2F2023%2F11%2Fattacks-arrests-threats-censorship-the-high-risks-of-reporting-the-israel-hamas-war%2F%5C%22%3ECommittee%20to%20Protect%20Journalists%20list%3C%2Fa%3E%20blames%20Israeli%20authorities%20for%20the%20vast%20majority%20of%20incidents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20October%2012%2C%20Israeli%20police%20assaulted%20a%20group%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-middle-east-67102956%5C%22%3EBBC%20journalists%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Tel%20Aviv%20and%20held%20them%20at%20gunpoint.%20The%20BBC%20said%20reporters%20Muhannad%20Tutunji%2C%20Haitham%20Abudiab%20and%20their%20BBC%20Arabic%20team%20were%20driving%20a%20vehicle%20clearly%20marked%20%E2%80%9CTV%E2%80%9D%20in%20red%20tape%2C%20and%20both%20Tutunji%20and%20Abudaib%20presented%20their%20press%20cards.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20October%2016%2C%20Israeli%20journalist%20and%20columnist%20Israel%20Frey%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DzMKyH4jCnTE%5C%22%3Ewent%20into%20hiding%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20a%20mob%20of%20far-right%20Israelis%20attacked%20his%20home%20the%20previous%20day.%20The%20mob%20was%20apparently%20angry%20at%20a%20column%20he%20wrote%20expressing%20sympathy%20for%20Palestinians%20in%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20November%205%2C%20Israeli%20police%20arrested%2030-year-old%20freelance%20Palestinian%20journalist%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.madacenter.org%2Fen%2Farticle%2F1449%2F%5C%22%3ESomaya%20Jawabra%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Nablus%20in%20the%20northern%20West%20Bank.%20She%20was%20summoned%2C%20along%20with%20her%20husband%2C%20journalist%20Tariq%20Al-Sarkaji%2C%20for%20an%20investigation.%20Her%20husband%20was%20later%20released%20but%20Jawabra%2C%20who%20is%20seven%20months%20pregnant%2C%20remains%20in%20detention.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ifj.org%2Fmedia-centre%2Fnews%2Fdetail%2Fcategory%2Fpress-releases%2Farticle%2Fglobal-call-israel-must-commit-to-protecting-journalists%5C%22%3EInternational%20Federation%20of%20Journalists%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20called%20on%20the%20Israeli%20government%20to%20rigorously%20observe%20international%20law%20that%20requires%20combatants%20to%20take%20all%20reasonable%20steps%20to%20treat%20journalists%20as%20civilians%20and%20safeguard%20their%20lives.%20The%20Israeli%20military%20has%20told%20at%20least%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fisraeli-military-says-it-cant-guarantee-journalists-safety-gaza-2023-10-27%2F%5C%22%3Etwo%20international%20news%20agencies%3C%2Fa%3E%20it%20cannot%20guarantee%20the%20safety%20of%20their%20staff%20covering%20the%20Gaza%20crisis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPropaganda%20war%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20matters%2C%20and%20not%20just%20to%20the%20reporters%20who%20are%20putting%20their%20lives%20on%20the%20line%20or%20being%20attacked%20and%20abused.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20our%20digitally%20connected%20world%2C%20distortions%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapnews.com%2Farticle%2Fisrael-hamas-gaza-misinformation-fact-check-e58f9ab8696309305c3ea2bfb269258e%5C%22%3Edisinformation%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20outright%20lies%20speed%20around%20the%20world%20faster%20than%20a%20ballistic%20missile.%20The%20online%20narrative%20is%20at%20least%20as%20important%20as%20the%20fighting%20on%20the%20ground%2C%20as%20each%20side%20works%20to%20portray%20itself%20as%20the%20victim%2C%20harnessing%20numbers%20and%20narratives%20to%20support%20their%20arguments%20and%20win%20backing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20has%20real%20consequences.%20In%20the%20propaganda%20war%2C%20public%20support%20translates%20to%20political%2C%20financial%20and%20even%20military%20aid.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20appears%20to%20be%20one%20reason%20why%20Israel%20has%20repeatedly%20imposed%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aljazeera.com%2Fnews%2F2023%2F11%2F1%2Fisrael-imposes-communication-blackout-on-gaza-second-time-in-five-days%5C%22%3Ecommunications%20blackouts%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Gaza.%20As%20the%20crisis%20draws%20on%2C%20painful%20stories%20about%20the%20consequences%20of%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20attacks%20erode%20public%20support%3B%20controlling%20the%20narrative%20becomes%20increasingly%20important.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20more%20journalists%20are%20killed%20or%20intimidated%20away%20from%20their%20work%2C%20the%20more%20space%20there%20is%20for%20the%20propagandists%20of%20both%20sides%20to%20work%20unhindered.%20Without%20good%20journalists%2C%20we%20are%20forced%20to%20rely%20on%20unchecked%20and%20unchallenged%20statements%20from%20protagonists%2C%20or%20unfiltered%20social%20media%20posts%20that%20create%20more%20confusion%20than%20clarity.%20Neither%20gives%20us%20a%20solid%20basis%20for%20understanding%20what%20is%20really%20going%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20is%20why%20good%20journalism%20is%20more%20important%20than%20ever.%20Journalists%20are%20not%20perfect%2C%20of%20course%2C%20but%20most%20trade%20on%20their%20credibility.%20They%20rely%20on%20well-established%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ifj.org%2Fwho%2Frules-and-policy%2Fglobal-charter-of-ethics-for-journalists%5C%22%3Eprofessional%20protocols%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20commit%20them%20to%20factual%20accuracy%2C%20independence%2C%20rights-of-reply%2C%20and%20so%20on.%20In%20the%20process%2C%20they%20give%20their%20work%20a%20degree%20of%20trust%20that%20keeps%20their%20readers%20and%20audiences%20coming%20back%20for%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECollectively%2C%20the%20goal%20is%20to%20create%20a%20core%20of%20information%20that%20is%20reliably%20independent%20and%20%E2%80%93%20as%20much%20as%20possible%20in%20a%20crisis%20as%20foggy%20as%20this%20one%20%E2%80%93%20broadly%20accurate.%20Without%20that%20commitment%2C%20journalists%20lose%20their%20authority%20and%20hence%20their%20value.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20issue%20is%20so%20crucial%20that%20the%20United%20Nations%20has%20created%20a%20special%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.unesco.org%2Fen%2Fsafety-journalists%2Fun-plan-action%3FTSPD_101_R0%3D080713870fab2000b574785dd284b33d415bcb7212995e0107d37fa39f2de85c400d7a9ae875e2aa086d8eb45714300025cd580abf3788c43674045df43bf91bb48d16fe7db539ad762bb44504efd0e165ad95941a05b1ede3b3b5347a9c949a%5C%22%3EPlan%20of%20Action%20on%20the%20Safety%20of%20Journalists%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20plan%20is%20now%20a%20decade%20old%2C%20and%20clearly%20not%20working%20as%20well%20as%20it%20should.%20The%20wars%20in%20Ukraine%20and%2