upon%2C%20using%20this%20massacre%20almost%20as%20an%20excuse%20or%20even%20%E2%80%9Copportunity%E2%80%9D%2C%20began%20to%20apply%20the%20heaviest%20state%20terror%20against%20the%20Palestinian%20people%20to%20date.%20In%20the%20midst%20of%20these%20massacres%2C%20we%20witnessed%20the%20constant%20bombing%20of%20hospitals%2C%20the%20complete%20destruction%20of%20two%20hospitals%2C%20the%20bombing%20of%20ambulance%20convoys%20and%20the%20open%20declaration%20of%20the%20Israeli%20state%20that%20it%20will%20not%20recognise%20any%20law%20of%20war.%20As%20of%20November%206%2C%20the%20death%20toll%20in%20Gaza%20is%20estimated%20to%20have%20exceeded%2010%2C000%2C%20including%20thousands%20of%20children%20and%20women.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Israeli%20government%20today%20uses%20Hamas%E2%80%99%20recent%20attacks%20as%20a%20pretext%20for%20its%20massacres%2C%20but%20we%20know%20that%20the%20Palestinian%20people%20have%20been%20subjected%20to%20intense%20repression%20and%20violence%20by%20the%20Israeli%20security%20forces%20even%20in%20the%20absence%20of%20Hamas.%20The%20Israeli%20government%2C%20which%20has%20been%20labelled%20an%20apartheid%20regime%20by%20many%20Jewish%20diaspora%20initiatives%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20as%20well%20as%20by%20political%20and%20civil%20initiatives%20of%20Israeli%20citizens%2C%20implies%20in%20front%20of%20the%20eyes%20of%20the%20world%20that%20it%20aims%20to%20wipe%20out%20the%20people%20of%20Gaza%2C%20estimated%20at%202.2%20million%2C%20from%20the%20face%20of%20the%20earth.%C2%A0%20The%20land%20operation%20launched%20by%20Israel%20amounts%20to%20ethnic%20cleansing%20and%20even%20genocide.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20are%20already%20witnessing%20the%20voices%20of%20many%20Israeli%20academics%2C%20journalists%20and%20thinkers%20who%20are%20speaking%20out%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20who%20are%20now%20being%20targeted%20and%20witch-hunted%20by%20their%20own%20state%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20for%20questioning%20the%20official%20narrative%20of%20the%20state.%20We%20heard%20the%20voices%20of%20these%20brave%20people%20who%20are%20speaking%20out%20against%20their%20own%20state%E2%80%99s%20unjust%20war%20and%20massacres%20during%20the%20Gaza%20bombardment%20in%202014%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E.%C2%A0%20It%20gives%20hope%20to%20see%20that%20the%20number%20of%20people%20joining%20this%20voice%20has%20increased%20exponentially%20after%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20massacres%20in%20Gaza%20today.%20As%20Academics%20for%20Peace%20from%20Turkey%2C%20we%20are%20well%20aware%20of%20the%20silencing%20and%20intimidation%20methods%20that%20states%20can%20use%20against%20dissenting%20voices%2C%20especially%20in%20extraordinary%20situations%20such%20as%20war%2C%20and%20therefore%20we%20stand%20in%20strong%20solidarity%20with%20both%20our%20Palestinian%20colleagues%20and%20our%20colleagues%20in%20Israel%20who%20speak%20out%20against%20the%20crimes%20of%20their%20state.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%2C%20the%20undersigned%20Academics%20for%20Peace%20from%20Turkey%2C%20call%20on%20the%20international%20public%2C%20politicians%20and%20media%20to%20take%20a%20stand%20against%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20massacres.%20We%20also%20call%20on%20Turkey%20to%20cut%20all%20military%2C%20commercial%20and%20diplomatic%20relations%20with%20Israel%20until%20the%20occupation%20ends%20and%20peace%20is%20established.%20As%20in%20all%20conflicts%20in%20the%20world%2C%20a%20lasting%20peace%20can%20only%20be%20secured%20if%20the%20oppressed%20have%20an%20equal%20say%20in%20peace%20negotiations.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Col%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3EA.%20Celil%20Kaya%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3EAdalet%20B.%20Alada%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3EAdnan%20%C5%9Eahin%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3EAhmet%20B%C3%BClent%20%C3%96zer%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3EAhmet%20%C3%87inici%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E