s%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThese%20are%20locutions%20straight%20out%20of%20the%20Zionist%20playbook%3A%20that%20an%20older%20scripture%20can%20assign%20rights%20denied%20to%20people%20in%20actual%20occupation%20of%20a%20land%20for%20centuries.%20That%20claim%20is%20on%20its%20face%2C%20as%20ludicrous%20as%20the%20foundational%20slogan%20of%20Zionism%2C%20that%20Palestine%20is%20a%20%E2%80%9Cland%20without%20a%20people%2C%20for%20a%20people%20without%20a%20land%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIf%20Kumaraswamy%20fails%20in%20the%20broader%20line%20of%20attack%2C%20his%20more%20specific%20points%20need%20attention%2C%20despite%20their%20evident%20spuriousness.%20He%20wonders%20for%20instance%2C%20if%20some%20of%20what%20Gandhi%20had%20to%20say%20on%20Israel%20went%20missing%20because%20of%20an%20effort%20at%20sanitising%20his%20prolific%20output.%20Pyarelal%2C%20his%20long-time%20personal%20secretary%2C%20is%20recorded%20telling%20the%20writer%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fyalebooks.yale.edu%2Fbook%2F9780300055399%2Fmahatma-gandhi-and-his-apostles%2F%5C%22%3EVed%20Mehta%3C%2Fa%3E%20rather%20%E2%80%9Cportentously%E2%80%9D%2C%20that%20in%20the%20vastness%20of%20material%20he%20was%20holding%20in%20trust%2C%20there%20was%20%E2%80%9Csome%E2%80%9D%20he%20decided%20to%20%E2%80%9Csuppress%E2%80%9D%2C%20such%20as%20%E2%80%9CGandhi%E2%80%99s%20views%20on%20Israel%E2%80%9D.%20There%20is%20no%20reason%20to%20believe%20that%20Pyarelal%20has%20been%20inaccurately%20recorded%20in%20Mehta%E2%80%99s%201976%20book%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20was%20followed%20by%20the%20rather%20cocky%20claim%20by%20Pyarelal%2C%20who%20died%20in%201982%2C%20that%20he%20held%20a%20unique%20power%20to%20decide%20how%20the%20public%20sees%20Gandhi%2C%20since%20%E2%80%9Cby%20God%E2%80%99s%20grace%E2%80%9D%2C%20he%20was%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20only%20one%20who%20knows%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EKumaraswamy%20concludes%20that%20we%20are%20left%20%E2%80%9Conly%20with%20a%20sanitised%20and%20politically%20correct%20version%E2%80%9D%2C%20which%20means%20we%20will%20never%20%E2%80%9Ccompletely%20understand%20how%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%20viewed%20and%20gradually%20shifted%20his%20position%20vis-%C3%A0-vis%20Palestine%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20has%20more%20to%20say%3A%20Gandhi%20is%20known%20to%20have%20met%20two%20Zionist%20leaders%20when%20he%20went%20to%20London%20for%20the%20Second%20Round%20Table%20Conference%20on%20India.%20But%20the%20record%20of%20these%20meetings%20is%20missing%20from%20his%20Collected%20Works.%20There%20is%20in%20fact%2C%20a%20complete%20absence%20of%20any%20record%20of%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20numerous%20meetings%20with%20Jewish%20leaders.%20Absence%20of%20evidence%2C%20he%20concludes%2C%20is%20not%20evidence%20of%20absence.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20midst%20of%20these%20scattershot%20insinuations%2C%20Kumaraswamy%20does%20draw%20attention%20to%20a%20specific%20absence.%20In%20July%201937%2C%20%E2%80%9CGandhi%20passed%20on%20an%20unsigned%20statement%20to%20the%20Jewish%20Agency%20in%20Palestine%20through%20Hermann%20Kallenbach%2C%20his%20comrade-in-arms%20during%20his%20South%20African%20days%E2%80%9D.%20This%20has%20gone%20%E2%80%9Cconspicuously%20missing%20in%20volume%2096%20of%20the%20Collected%20Works%2C%20devoted%20exclusively%20to%20the%20Kallenbach%20Papers%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EGandhi%20and%20Kallenbach%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20the%20conspiratorially%20minded%2C%20the%20point%20may%20seem%20significant%2C%20though%20ultimately%20it%20is%20of%20little%20consequence.%20Kallenbach%E2%80%99s%20visit%20to%20India%20in%201937%20and%20his%20very%20fond%20reunion%20with%20Gandhi%20after%2023%20years%2C%20is%20dealt%20with%20in%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FGreat_Soul%3A_Mahatma_Gandhi_and_