1%2F768x432%2Fskynews-hezbollah-lebanon_6356969.png%3F20231111213804%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fat-hezbollahs-martyrs-day-commemoration-their-leader-threatens-escalation-13006033%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Operational%20security%20is%20always%20tight%20when%20the%20most%20powerful%20political%20and%20military%20faction%20in%20Lebanon%20organises%20an%20event.%C2%A0%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A181%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fat-hezbollahs-martyrs-day-commemoration-their-leader-threatens-escalation-13006033%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fat-hezbollahs-martyrs-day-commemoration-their-leader-threatens-escalation-13006033%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fat-hezbollahs-martyrs-day-commemoration-their-leader-threatens-escalation-13006033%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Backstory%3A%20It's%20Time%20Journalists%20Woke%20Up%20to%20Their%20Digital%20Security%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F10%2F23203159%2FScreen-Shot-2020-10-23-at-8.31.43-PM.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EOctober%2031%2C%202022%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20The%20Delhi%20Police%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fthe-wires-statement-on-seizure-of-electronic-devices-by-delhi-police-crime-branch%5C%22%3Eraided%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20homes%20of%20%3Cem%3ET%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3Ehe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99s%20founding%20editors%2C%20deputy%20editor%2C%20and%20business%20head%2C%20taking%20away%20phones%2C%20computers%2C%20and%20iPads.%20Hard%20disks%20from%20two%20computers%20used%20by%20accounts%20staff%20were%20also%20seized.%20The%20raiding%20teams%20reportedly%20sought%20and%20took%2C%20passwords%20to%20official%20and%20personal%20email%20accounts%20belonging%20to%20one%20or%20more%20staffers%2C%20and%20asked%20some%20of%20those%20raided%20to%20disable%20passcodes%20from%20their%20devices.%20According%20to%20sources%20at%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20no%20hash%20value%20(a%20unique%20numerical%20value%20issued%20to%20maintain%20the%20integrity%20of%20digital%20data)%20or%20cloned%20copy%20was%20given%20at%20the%20time%20of%20seizure.%20(Source%3A%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EOctober%203%2C%202023%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Special%20Cell%20of%20the%20Delhi%20Police%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fdelhi-police-conducts-early-morning-raids-at-houses-of-journalists-satirists%5C%22%3Econducted%20raids%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20various%20locations%20including%20%3Cem%3ENewsClick%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99s%20offices%2C%20residences%20of%20journalists%20and%20employees%20%E2%80%93%20past%20and%20present%2C%20consultants%2C%20and%20freelance%20contributors%20associated%20with%20%3Cem%3ENewsClick%3C%2Fem%3E.%C2%A0FIRs%20were%20not%20provided%2C%20nor%20were%20the%20particulars%20of%20the%20alleged%20offences%20made%20available.%20Electronic%20devices%20were%20seized%20without%20any%20adherence%20to%20due%20process%20such%20as%20the%20provision%20of%20seizure%20memos%2C%20hash%20values%20of%20the%20seized%20data%2C%20or%20even%20copies%20of%20the%20data%20seized.%20(Source%3A%20%3Cem%3ENewsClick%3C%2Fem%3E)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20year%20separated%20these%20two%20raids%20on%20media%20establishments.%20What%20is%20striking%20is%20the%20similarity%20of%20the%20modus%20operandi%20adopted%20by%20the%20Delhi%20Police.%20In%20both%20instances%2C%20there%20was%20a%20complete%20disregard%20for%20even%20the%20most%20basic%20norms%20laid%20down%20in%20numerous%20court%20verdicts.%20They%20also%20point%20to%20the%20sharply%20asymmetric%20power%20relations%20between%20the%20police%20and%20the%20journalists%20under%20scrutiny.%20These%20are%20tactics%20that%20recall%20the%20Gestapo-like%20methods%20of%20the%20Israeli%20National%20Police%20and%20the%20Law%20Enforcement%20Command%20of%20the%20Islamic%20Republic%20of%20%3Cem%3EIran.%20%3C%2Fem%3EDespite%20the%20political%20hostility%20between%20Iran%20and%20Israel%2C%20both%20law%20enforcement%20models%20share%20a%20common%20bestiality%20of%20approach.%20%E2%80%9CYou%20can%20give%20us%20your%20password%20the%20easy%20way%2C%20or%20the%20hard%20way%2C%E2%80%9D%20an%20Iranian%20journalist%20recalled%20being%20told%2C%20in%20an%20interaction%20with%20the%20Committee%20to%20Protect%20Journalists%20during%20the%20protests%20that%20followed%20the%20death%20of%20Mahsa%20Amini.%20The%20%E2%80%9Chard%E2%80%9D%20way%20can%20well%20be%20imagined.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F12%2Fpress-freedom-1.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221160%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-208094%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22870%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ERepresentative%20image.%20Photo%3A%20Karnika%20Kohli%2FThe%20Wire%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECloser%20home%2C%20during%20the%20%3Cem%3ENewsClick%3C%2Fem%3E%20raids%2C%20the%20police%20came%20away%20with%20some%20250%20devices%20seized%20from%2090%20journalists%20without%20the%20hash%20values%20of%20these%20seized%20electronic%20items%20being%20given%20to%20even%20one%20of%20them.%20A%20journalist%20who%20was%20raided%20revealed%20the%20trauma%20it%20had%20caused%20in%20a%20conversation%20with%20me%3A%20%E2%80%9CImagine%20seven%20or%20eight%20burly%20men%20turning%20up%20at%20your%20doorstep%20early%20in%20the%20morning.%20When%20asked%20for%20a%20warrant%2C%20they%20produce%20a%20sheet%20of%20white%20paper%20indicating%20in%20a%20few%20lines%20that%20a%20search%20and%20seizure%20operation%20has%20been%20ordered%20under%20the%20authority%20of%20the%20ACP%20of%20the%20Special%20Cell%2C%20Delhi%20Police.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20is%20so%20totally%20intimidated%2C%20one%20cannot%20even%20think%20straight.%20You%20find%20yourself%20blindly%20submitting%20to%20everything%20demanded%2C%20from%20providing%20access%20to%20all%20your%20papers%2C%20certificates%2C%20even%20those%20related%20to%20ownership%20of%20personal%20property.%20Documents%20of%20identification%2C%20including%20passports%2C%20were%20asked%20for%2C%20and%20taken.%20Passwords%20and%20pin%20numbers%20to%20devices%20were%20demanded%20and%20meekly%20surrendered.%20There%20was%20no%20way%20one%20could%20contact%20one%E2%80%99s%20colleagues%20and%20ask%20for%20advice%20because%20my%20mobile%20phone%20was%20now%20in%20the%20hands%20of%20the%20police%20officer%20and%20that%20was%20the%20last%20time%20I%20saw%20it.%20I%20felt%20I%20had%20become%20a%20non-person%2C%20stripped%20of%20my%20rights%2C%20my%20dignity%20and%20my%20ability%20to%20carry%20on%20%E2%80%93%20not%20just%20with%20my%20work%2C%20but%20my%20life.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fnewsclick-raids-shrinking-press-freedom-democratic-backslide-south-asia%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98NewsClick%20Raids%20Emblematic%20of%20Shrinking%20Press%20Freedom%2C%20Democratic%20Backslide%20in%20South%20Asia%E2%80%99%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20experiences%20like%20this%20that%20have%20gone%20to%20inform%20a%20crucial%20petition%20filed%20before%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20of%20India%20by%20five%20academics%20and%20the%20Foundation%20for%20Media%20Professionals%20(%E2%80%98%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fdevice-seizures-making-a-mockery-of-landmark-privacy-ruling%5C%22%3EDevice%20Seizures%20Are%20Making%20a%20Mockery%20of%20The%20Supreme%20Court%E2%80%99s%20Landmark%20Privacy%20Ruling%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%99%2C%20October%2017).%20The%20petition%20suggests%20guidelines%20for%20such%20search%20and%20seizure%20interventions%20based%20on%20constitutional%20rights%20and%20Supreme%20Court%20verdicts.%20It%20emphasises%20that%20%E2%80%9Cseizure%20of%20electronic%20devices%20must%20take%20place%20only%20after%20a%20judicial%20warrant%E2%80%9D%2C%20with%20emergency%20seizure%20being%20the%20exception%20rather%20than%20the%20rule%20and%20obtained%20only%20after%20reasons%20for%20such%20emergency%20action%20are%20cited.%20It%20ruled%20out%20any%20seizure%20made%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20conjecture%20over%20the%20possibility%20of%20evidence%20being%20found.%20Should%20a%20device%20be%20seized%2C%20it%20must%20first%20be%20subjected%20to%20an%20initial%20examination%20by%20an%20independent%20agency%20in%20the%20presence%20of%20the%20owner%20of%20the%20device.%20Importantly%2C%20all%20%E2%80%9Cirrelevant%2C%20personal%20and%20privileged%20material%E2%80%9D%20would%20need%20to%20be%20separately%20identified%20with%20the%20investigating%20agency%20being%20entitled%20only%20to%20a%20copy%20of%20the%20relevant%20material.%20The%20device%20itself%20must%20be%20returned%20immediately%20thereupon.%20Further%2C%20the%20owners%20of%20devices%20which%20are%20sought%20to%20be%20seized%20cannot%20be%20compelled%20to%20divulge%20any%20credentials%20or%20passwords%2C%20or%20information.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20case%20is%20still%20being%20heard%20but%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20in%20its%20initial%20response%20to%20the%20counter-arguments%20raised%20by%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20lawyers%2C%20acknowledged%20that%20this%20is%20indeed%20a%20very%20serious%20issue%20and%20guidelines%20protecting%20journalists%20from%20arbitrary%20seizures%20need%20to%20be%20in%20place%20(%E2%80%98%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fproper-guidelines-seizure-of-digital-devices-journalists-supreme-court%5C%22%3ENeed%20Proper%20Guidelines%20for%20Seizure%20of%20Digital%20Devices%20of%20Journalists%3A%20Supreme%20Court%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%99%2C%20November%207).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20conspicuous%20rise%20in%20the%20targeting%20of%20journalists%20by%20the%20Modi%20government%20points%20to%20wider%20anxiety%20that%20the%20narrative%20it%20has%20successfully%20created%20and%20furthered%20through%20coopted%20corporate%20media%20is%20being%20undone%20by%20those%20journalists%20it%20targets%20as%20anti-national.%20The%20pattern%20of%20stigmatising%20independent%20journalists%20had%20been%20set%20as%20early%20as%202015%2C%20a%20year%20after%20the%20Modi%20government%20came%20to%20power%2C%20when%20one%20minister%20came%20up%20with%20a%20slur%2C%20%E2%80%9Cpresstitute%E2%80%9D%2C%20coined%20by%20US-based%20Gerald%20Celente%2C%20against%20those%20who%20critiqued%20his%20style%20of%20functioning.%20Since%20then%20the%20Sanghi%20troll%20army%2C%20which%20functions%20as%20this%20government%E2%80%99s%20virtual%20praetorian%20guard%2C%20has%20come%20up%20with%20many%20more%20attack%20words%2C%20including%20the%20ubiquitous%20%E2%80%9Curban%20naxals%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20not%20surprising%20then%20that%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fapple-india-state-sponsored-spyware%5C%22%3EApple%20notice%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20about%20two%20dozen%20Indians%20warning%20them%20that%20their%20devices%20have%20been%20%E2%80%9Ccompromised%20by%20a%20state-sponsored%20attack%E2%80%9D%20included%20at%20least%20three%20journalists%20(the%20founder%20editor%20of%20this%20news%20portal%20and%20the%20investigative%20reporter%20who%20broke%20the%20story%20on%20Adani%E2%80%99s%20stock%20manipulation%20were%20in%20the%20list).%20Such%20attempts%20to%20stymie%20the%20opposition%20and%20the%20free%20media%20could%20get%20even%20more%20pernicious%20as%20the%202024%20general%20election%20draws%20closer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApar%20Gupta%2C%20who%20heads%20a%20digital%20rights%20advocacy%20group%2C%20Internet%20Freedom%20Foundation%2C%20points%20out%20that%20the%20Indian%20government%2C%20which%20has%20neither%20denied%20nor%20accepted%20that%20it%20has%20used%20the%20Pegasus%20spyware%20in%20the%20past%2C%20is%20today%20actively%20in%20the%20hunt%20for%20new%20spyware%2C%20with%20the%20%3Cem%3EFinancial%20Times%20%3C%2Fem%3Ereporting%20that%20India%20is%20%E2%80%9Cseeking%20new%20spyware%20contracts%20starting%20at%20approximately%20%2416%20million%20and%20potentially%20escalating%20to%20%24120%20million%20in%20the%20next%20few%20years.%20These%20contracts%20involve%20companies%20like%20the%20Intellexa%20Alliance%2C%20recently%20featured%20in%20a%20report%20called%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amnesty.org%2Fen%2Fdocuments%2Fact10%2F7245%2F2023%2Fen%2F%5C%22%3EThe%20Predator%20Files%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0(%E2%80%98%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fapple-india-state-sponsored-spyware%23%3A~%3Atext%3DNew%2520Delhi%253A%2520Multiple%2520top%2520leaders%2Cwith%2520your%2520Apple%2520ID%2520%25E2%2580%25A6.%25E2%2580%259D%5C%22%3EApple%20Warns%20Top%20Indian%20Opposition%20Leaders%2C%20Journalists%20About%20%E2%80%98State-Sponsored%E2%80%99%20Attack%20on%20Phone%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%99%2C%20October%2031).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F31110556%2Fcollage9.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F31110556%2Fcollage9.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F31110556%2Fcollage9-300x120.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F31110556%2Fcollage9-1024x410.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-682631%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EClockwise%20from%20top%20L%3A%20Mahua%20Moitra%2C%20Shashi%20Tharoor%2C%20Siddharth%20Varadarajan%2C%20Sitaram%20Yechury%2C%20Priyanka%20Chaturvedi%2C%20Akhilesh%20Yadav.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20are%20living%20through%20odd%20and%20uneven%20times%2C%20where%20the%20instinct%20to%20control%20is%20swathed%20in%20a%20thick%20layer%20of%20opacity.%20A%20brilliant%20exposition%20recently%20carried%20in%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20unpacked%20the%20draft%20legislations%20that%20the%20Modi%20administration%20has%20introduced%20which%20purportedly%20seeks%20to%20reform%20and%20de-colonise%20the%20legal%20framework%20for%20criminal%20justice%20(%E2%80%98%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fthe-three-criminal-law-bills-using-criminal-law-to-establish-permanent-extra-constitutional-emergency-powers%5C%22%3EThe%20Three%20Criminal%20Law%20Bills%3A%20Using%20Criminal%20Law%20to%20Establish%20Permanent%20Extra-Constitutional%20Emergency%20Powers%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%99%2C%20November%201).%20The%20writer%20points%20out%20that%20contrary%20to%20the%20claims%20made%2C%20these%20drafts%20actually%20introduce%20a%20%E2%80%9Cdozen%20chilling%20changes%20to%20the%20law%20that%20have%20the%20potential%20to%20liquidate%20liberty%2C%20decimate%20democracy%20and%20fundamentally%20change%20the%20face%20of%20our%20polity%20from%20democratic%20to%20authoritarian%20should%20the%20government%20decide%20to%20deploy%20any%20or%20all%20of%20these%20changes%20to%20their%20fullest%20extent%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELike%20the%20all-seeing%20owl%20that%20can%20pierce%20the%20darkness%20with%20its%20gaze%2C%20it%20is%20only%20the%20independent%20media%20that%20can%20expose%20the%20opacity%20of%20government%20functioning.%20Attempts%20to%20hobble%20journalists%20through%20cynically%20designed%20laws%20and%20sweeping%20police%20powers%2C%20robbing%20them%20of%20their%20rights%2C%20end%20up%20grossly%20undermining%20the%20rights%20and%20liberties%20of%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECounting%20the%20crackdowns%2C%20state%20by%20state%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%20is%20an%20important%20backward%20glance%20as%20five%20states%20go%20to%20polls.%20How%20have%20the%20governments%20of%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Mizoram%2C%20Rajasthan%2C%20and%20Telangana%20fared%20in%20terms%20of%20Article%2019%201(a)%20constitutional%20guarantee%2C%20which%20is%20synonymous%20with%20free%20media%3F%20Over%20the%20years%2C%20the%20Free%20Speech%20Collective%20(FSC)%20Collective%20has%20been%20garnering%20data%20through%20systematic%20state-wise%20monitoring%2C%20and%20now%20on%20the%20eve%20of%20the%20state%20elections%2C%20it%20has%20come%20out%20with%20an%20important%20ready-reckoner.%20Entitled%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffreespeechcollective.in%2Ffree-speech-in-the-states%2F%5C%22%3EBetween%20Electoral%20Rhetoric%20and%20Ground%20Reality%20Free%20Speech%20in%20the%20States%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%2C%20it%20has%20been%20authored%20by%20four%20senior%20journalists%20and%20free%20speech%20activists%2C%20Geeta%20Seshu%2C%20Laxmi%20Murthy%2C%20Malini%20Subramaniam%2C%20and%20Sarita%20Ramamoorthy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20touches%20upon%20a%20gamut%20of%20issues%20ranging%20from%20assassinations%20of%20journalists%20and%20internet%20shutdowns%2C%20to%20the%20silencing%20of%20dissent%20through%20other%20ways%20including%20the%20overuse%2Fmisuse%20of%20laws.%20The%20last%20category%20has%20come%20to%20be%20known%20as%20%E2%80%98lawfare%E2%80%99%2C%20defined%20as%20the%20%E2%80%9Cuse%20of%20legal%20systems%20and%20institutions%20to%20damage%20or%20delegitimise%20an%20opponent%2C%20or%20to%20deter%20an%20individual%E2%80%99s%20usage%20of%20their%20legal%20rights%E2%80%9D.%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20in%20particular%2C%20made%20full%20use%20of%20this%20method%20of%20punishment%20with%20journalists%20being%20charged%20under%20multiple%20sections%20of%20the%20law%20for%20reporting%20on%20sand%20mining%20and%20other%20local%20level%20corruption.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EData%20from%20all%20five%20states%20indicate%20some%20obvious%20commonalities.%20Detentions%20and%20arrests%20of%20journalists%20have%20been%20steadily%20rising%2C%20with%20Telangana%20reporting%20the%20second%20largest%20number%20of%20such%20cases%20in%20the%20country%20%E2%80%93%2040%20cases%20over%20these%20five%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMadhya%20Pradesh%2C%20the%20report%20notes%2C%20has%20become%20a%20%E2%80%9Claboratory%20of%20sorts%20for%20academic%20censorship%E2%80%9D.%20It%20has%20also%20not%20been%20able%20to%20provide%20a%20secure%20environment%20for%20journalism%20as%20the%202020%20killings%20of%20Vikram%20Joshi%2C%20and%20a%20little%20later%20of%20Sunil%20Tiwari%2C%20indicate.%20MP%20also%20saw%20the%20ruthlessness%20of%20the%20state%20in%20cracking%20down%20on%20crime%20reporter%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fattack-on-press-freedom-in-madhya-pradesh-continues-as-cm-tries-to-appease-journalists-before-polls%5C%22%3EJaalam%20Singh%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20noted%20for%20his%20integrity.%20For%20daring%20to%20expose%20the%20criminal%20acts%20of%20politicians%20aligned%20with%20the%20ruling%20party%2C%20he%20had%20a%20succession%20of%20back-to-back%20cases%20(11%20at%20last%20count)%20filed%20against%20him%20in%20different%20districts%20of%20the%20Gwalior%20division.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENew%20ways%20of%20punishing%20journalists%20also%20surfaced.%20The%20Telangana%20government%20resorted%20to%20bulldozer%20action%20on%20May%2022%2C%202020%2C%20to%20destroy%20the%20home%20of%20Shanigarapu%20Parameshwar%2C%20a%20television%20journalist%2C%20who%20had%20reported%20on%20a%20local%20politician%20having%20hosted%20a%20birthday%20party%20at%20which%20500%20of%20his%20supporters%20were%20in%20attendance%20at%20the%20height%20of%20the%20pandemic%20lockdown.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20almost%20every%20state%20saw%20the%20use%20of%20internet%20shutdowns%2C%20some%20were%20more%20blatant%20in%20wielding%20this%20tool.%20Rajasthan%20was%20a%20particularly%20egregious%20violator.%20In%20these%20five%20years%2C%20there%20were%20at%20least%2060%20internet%20shutdowns.%20The%20Collective%20notes%20that%20Rajasthan%20was%20one%20of%20five%20states%20challenged%20in%20a%20petition%20filed%20before%20the%20apex%20court%20by%20the%20Software%20Freedom%20Law%20Centre%20last%20year%2C%20which%20pointed%20out%20that%20such%20shutdowns%20are%20an%20arbitrary%20exercise%20of%20the%20law%20and%20go%20against%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20ruling%20that%20the%20right%20to%20freedom%20of%20speech%20and%20expression%20and%20the%20right%20to%20carry%20on%20business%20using%20the%20medium%20of%20internet%20is%20constitutionally%20protected.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJournalists%20in%20Mizoram%2C%20being%20a%20border%20state%2C%20have%20their%20own%20specific%20challenges%20including%20personal%20attacks.%20Some%20have%20revealed%20how%20self-censorship%20has%20become%20a%20norm%2C%20given%20the%20sharp%20political%20divisions%20that%20mark%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EReaders%20write%20in%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDoes%20Israel%20need%20Gandhi%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EA%20rejoinder%20from%20Dr.%20Sandeep%20Shede%2C%20marketing%20and%20business%20strategy%20consultant%3A%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fem%3EYour%20thoughts%20on%20the%20Israel%20%26amp%3B%20Hamas%20Conflict%20are%20really%20thought-provoking%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20one%20of%20the%20worst-researched%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fbackstory-what-was-the-indian-media-doing-when-a-genocide-was-playing-out-in-gaza%5C%22%3Earticles%3C%2Fa%3E%20I%20have%20read%20in%20my%20entire%20life.%20The%20writer%20seems%20extremely%20confused%20with%20so%20many%20facts%20that%20are%20irrelevant%20to%20the%20conflict.%20The%20portrayal%20of%20Indian%20media%20was%20blatantly%20exaggerated%20to%20an%20inexcusable%20point.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20world%20wants%20to%20know%20the%20following%20things%3A%20What%20has%20Hamas%20got%20in%20this%20conflict%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDoes%20the%20%3Cem%3EWire.in%3C%2Fem%3E%20have%20access%20to%20Hamas%20in%20Gaza%3F%C2%A0Does%20the%20%3Cem%3EWire.in%3C%2Fem%3E%20gather%20input%20on%20who%20finances%20the%20Hamas%3F%20Does%20the%20%3Cem%3EWire.in%3C%2Fem%3E%20gather%20the%20inputs%20on%20who%20armed%20Hamas%3F%20Does%20the%20%3Cem%3EWire.in%3C%2Fem%3E%20track%20the%20movement%20of%20weapons%20of%20mass%20destruction%20from%20outside%20the%20world%C2%A0into%20Gaza%3F%20Does%20the%20%3Cem%3EWire.in%3C%2Fem%3E%20gather%20the%20input%20on%20the%20400%20km%20of%20tunnels%20and%20hideouts%20of%20Hamas%20in%20Gaza%3F%20Does%20the%20%3Cem%3EWire.in%3C%2Fem%3E%20gather%20the%20input%20on%20selective%20journalism%C2%A0that%20is%20done%20about%20Gaza%20now%3F%20Do%20you%20believe%20Israel%20needs%20Gandhi%20for%20peaceful%20non-violent%20resistance%20in%20this%20campaign%20against%20uncivilised%20Hamas%20terrorists%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThese%20undemocratic%20Islamic%20countries%20of%20the%20Middle%20East%20have%20been%20a%20real%20threat%20to%20Israel%20since%20its%20inception%20in%201948.%20And%20the%20autocrats%20ruling%20these%20Islamic%20countries%20are%20kings%20and%20princes%20in%20the%2021st%20century.%20They%20are%20collectively%20fighting%20with%20Israel%20through%20religious%20terrorist%20proxies%20who%20term%20this%20a%20religious%20war.%20A%20jihad%20against%20all%20Jews%3F%20Do%20you%20believe%20it%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHamas%20is%20still%20continuing%20the%20attack%20even%20today%20and%20has%20not%20released%20the%20hostages.%20Israel%20will%20provide%20a%20befitting%20counterattack%20to%20them%20in%20order%20to%20maintain%20its%20existence.%20Israelis%20know%20that.%20Seven%20million%20Jews%20were%20killed%20by%20Nazi%20Germany%20from%201934%20to%201945%20while%20practicing%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20peaceful%20non-violent%20resistance.%20This%20is%202023%2C%20the%20Israeli%20counterattack%20has%20just%20started%2C%20so%20don%E2%80%99t%20get%20into%20panic%20mode.%20Former%20US%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20has%20spoken%20at%20the%20Republican%20Jewish%20Coalition%20Conference%3A%20%E2%80%98If%20you%20spill%20a%20drop%20of%20American%20blood%2C%20we%20will%20spill%20a%20gallon%20of%20yours%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAnd%20Israelis%20may%20come%20up%20with%20new%20war%20fronts%20with%20Islamic%20countries%20that%20intend%20to%20wipe%20Israel%20off%20the%20world%20map.%20Also%2C%20Hezbollah%20and%20others%20are%20already%20compelled%20by%20Israel%20to%20join%20the%20existing%20Israel%20and%20Hamas%20conflict.%20Given%20this%2C%20it%20seems%20a%20well-planned%2C%20systemic%20%C2%A0and%20strategic%20approach%20by%20Israel%20to%20destroy%20the%20%E2%80%98Axis%20of%20Resistance%E2%80%99%20led%20by%20Hezbollah%20and%20others%20in%20this%20conflict%20itself.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EMy%20response%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%3A%3C%2Fem%3E%20Thank%20you%20Dr.%20Shede%20for%20your%20mail.%20While%20you%20are%20entitled%20to%20your%20views%2C%20I%20find%20it%20incredulous%20that%20in%20all%20those%20questions%20you%20raised%20about%20the%20emergence%20of%20Hamas%2C%20you%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20even%20one%20involving%20Israel%20and%20how%20it%20came%20to%20exist%20on%20land%20that%20belonged%20to%20the%20Palestinians.%20How%20did%20it%20come%20to%20rule%20through%20dispossession%20of%20Palestinians%20and%20everyday%20torture%3F%20How%20did%20it%20come%20to%20possess%20nuclear%20weapons%3F%20How%20did%20its%20military%20become%20the%20fourth%20largest%20in%20the%20world%3F%20How%20does%20it%20get%20away%20after%20grievously%20violating%20international%20humanitarian%20law%20in%20its%20war%20against%20Gaza%3F%20While%20Hamas%20cannot%20be%20in%20any%20way%20be%20exonerated%20for%20what%20it%20did%20on%20October%207%20and%20for%20its%20fundamentalist%20ideology%2C%20Israel%20is%20today%20a%20settler%20colonial%20state%20that%20practices%20racist%20apartheid%20as%20state%20policy.%20Your%20patent%20lack%20of%20curiosity%20about%20how%20such%20a%20state%20even%20emerged%20is%20possibly%20why%20you%20endorse%20so%20full-throatedly%20the%20genocide%20it%20has%20perpetrated%20on%20Gaza%20for%20over%20a%20month%20now.%20The%20blood%20lust%20is%20further%20reflected%20in%20your%20admiration%20for%20the%20Donald%20Trump%20quote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbout%20the%20Indian%20media%2C%20you%20do%20not%20present%20any%20evidence%20to%20suggest%20that%20my%20critique%20was%20exaggerated.%20Since%20the%20column%20came%20out%2C%20information%20has%20emerged%20that%20the%20Israeli%20military%20facilitated%20the%20visits%20to%20Israel%20of%20the%20Indian%20media%20and%20provided%20hospitality%20and%20free%20visas%20to%20the%20women%20and%20men%20who%20went%20there.%20None%20of%20this%20is%20acknowledged%20publicly%20on%20the%20channels%20that%20accepted%20this%20and%20proceeded%20to%20provide%20a%20reportage%20that%20was%20completely%20Israel-centric.%20They%20don%E2%80%99t%20even%20carry%20searing%20newsfeed%20from%20Gaza%20in%20the%20aftermath%20of%20the%20Israeli%20invasion.%20As%20someone%20put%20it%2C%20multiple%20media%20outlets%20and%20journalists%2C%20especially%20in%20India%2C%20have%20made%20it%20abundantly%20clear%20they%20do%20not%20believe%20Palestinians%20are%20humans.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98We%20have%20stopped%20watching%20Indian%20channels%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EMalcolm%20Printer%3A%20%E2%80%9CI%20read%20your%20excellent%20piece%20on%20the%20Indian%20media%E2%80%99s%20one-sided%20coverage%20of%20the%20inhuman%20atrocities%20in%20Gaza%20today.%20Many%20Indians%20like%20me%20have%20long%20since%20stopped%20watching%20Indian%20channels%20due%20to%20their%20pervasive%20biases%20and%20lack%20of%20basic%20journalistic%20ethics.%20Instead%2C%20I%20have%20replaced%20them%20with%20sources%20like%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20which%20has%20rendered%20yeoman%20service%20to%20the%20discerning%20reader%20and%20viewer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20present%20genocide%20being%20furthered%20in%20Gaza%20and%20the%20West%20Bank%2C%20the%20insightful%20Karan%20Thapar%20interviews%20have%20been%20truly%20eye-opening.%20I%20congratulate%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20for%20going%20the%20extra%20mile%20in%20covering%20the%20other%20side%20of%20this%20ghastly%20carnage.%C2%A0You%20will%20be%20pleased%20to%20know%20that%20it%20is%20largely%20because%20of%20this%20objective%20reporting%20that%20my%20views%20on%20the%20perpetrator%C2%A0and%20victim%3B%20terroriser%20and%20terrorised%20in%20this%20unending%20conflict%20have%20undergone%20an%20informed%20rationalisation%20and%2C%20even%2C%C2%A0a%20reversal.%C2%A0Thank%20you%20and%20keep%20up%20the%20good%20work!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EText%20and%20image%20must%20be%20in%20sync%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ESushil%20Ahuja%20writes%3A%3C%2Fem%3E%20%E2%80%9CI%20would%20like%20you%20to%20note%20that%20while%20the%20stories%20from%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20are%20excellent%20and%20trustworthy%2C%20the%20photographs%20that%20accompany%20them%20seem%20out%20of%20balance.%20We%20in%20India%20tend%20to%20get%20impressed%20by%20headlines%20and%20mismatched%20photographs.%20The%20stories%20tell%20the%20truth%20but%20photographs%20tell%20the%20opposite.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EMy%20response%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%3A%20%3C%2Fem%3ENot%20sure%20what%20you%20mean%20by%20photographs%20misleading%20the%20reader.%20It%20would%20have%20been%20more%20useful%20if%20you%20had%20provided%20instances%20of%20such%20a%20mismatch.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EEndnote%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EIsrael%E2%80%99s%20war%20on%20Gaza%20has%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20a%20war%20on%20children.%20It%20has%20also%20been%20a%20war%20against%20journalists%20with%20a%20death%20toll%20estimated%20at%20anything%20between%2030%20and%2050%2C%20many%20of%20whom%20have%20also%20lost%20their%20family%20members.%20Silencing%20journalists%20is%20now%20a%20deliberate%20strategy%20of%20the%20Israel%20Defense%20Force.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20November%209%2C%20over%20750%20journalists%20wrote%20an%20open%20letter%20condemning%20what%20was%20termed%20as%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20slaughter%20of%20our%20colleagues%20and%20their%20families%20by%20the%20Israeli%20military%20and%20government%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0It%20notes%20that%20%E2%80%9CReporters%20in%20the%20besieged%20Gaza%20Strip%20are%20contending%20with%20extensive%20power%20outages%2C%20food%20and%20water%20shortages%20and%20a%20breakdown%20of%20the%20medical%20system.%20They%20have%20been%20killed%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Frsf.org%2Fen%2Fisraelpalestine-war-41-journalists-more-one-day-killed-first-month-israel-palestine-war%5C%22%3Ewhile%20visibly%20working%20as%20press%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20as%20well%20as%20at%20night%20in%20their%20homes.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ETragic%20times%2C%20but%20let%20me%20not%20forget%20to%20wish%20readers%20a%20very%20happy%20Diwali!%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWrite%20to%20%3Cem%3Eombudsperson%40thewire.in%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699712889000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F10%2F23203159%2FScreen-Shot-2020-10-23-at-8.31.43-PM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fbackstory-its-time-journalists-woke-up-to-their-digital-security%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20fortnightly%20column%20from%20The%20Wire's%20ombudsperson.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A18%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fbackstory-its-time-journalists-woke-up-to-their-digital-security%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Malayalam%20Film%20'Aattam'%20Shows%20How%20the%20Truth%20Can%20be%20Messy%20and%20Complicated%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F11173301%2FThe-Wire-75.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHow%20many%20more%20lies%20do%20I%20need%20to%20tell%20to%20prove%20to%20everyone%20that%20I%E2%80%99m%20telling%20the%20truth%3F%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20visibly%20shaken%20Anjali%20(Zarin%20Shihab)%20asks%20Vinay%20(Vinay%20Forrt)%20in%20Anand%20Ekarshi%E2%80%99s%20Malayalam%20film%2C%20%3Cem%3EAattam%20(The%20Play)%3C%2Fem%3E.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20loaded%20and%20absolutely%20necessary%20question%20for%20our%20paradoxical%20times%3A%20when%20humility%20is%20bragged%20about%2C%20solitude%20is%20an%20aesthetic%20to%20be%20exhibited%20to%20crowds%20on%20social%20media%2C%20and%20where%20a%20victim%20needs%20to%20be%20perfect%2C%20while%20empathy%20and%20nuance%20are%20lopsided%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20accused.%20The%20truth%20needs%20to%20be%20unblemished%20and%20padded%20with%20just%20the%20right%20amount%20of%20believability.%20Few%20want%20to%20grapple%20with%20the%20messy%2C%20contradictory%20nature%20of%20%3Cem%3Ethe%3C%2Fem%3E%20truth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnjali%20is%20an%20interior%20designer%2C%20who%20has%20been%20pursuing%20her%20love%20for%20acting%20as%20a%20part%20of%20a%20theatre%20group%20for%20over%2016%20years.%20She%E2%80%99s%20the%20only%20girl%20in%20the%20cast.%20Ekarshi%20addresses%20it%20early%20on%20in%20the%20film%20when%20a%20journalist%20poses%20the%20question%20to%20the%20director%20of%20the%20play%20in%20the%20film%20%E2%80%93%20%E2%80%9CWhy%20is%20there%20just%20one%20girl%20in%20the%20cast%3F%E2%80%9D%20Like%20most%20things%20here%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20very%20deliberate%20choice.%20The%20lead%20actor%20in%20the%20play%2C%20Hari%20(Kalabhavan%20Shahjohn)%20%E2%80%93%20depicted%20as%20a%20moderately-famous%20movie%20star%2C%20who%20joined%20the%20group%20two%20years%20ago%20%E2%80%93%20invites%20a%20few%20British%20friends%20to%20their%20performance.%20They%E2%80%99re%20so%20impressed%20by%20the%20play%20that%20they%20offer%20their%20villa%20to%20the%20group%20for%20a%20post-performance%20celebration.%20The%20entire%20group%20meets%20at%20the%20villa%2C%20and%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20evening%20is%20doused%20in%20alcohol%20and%20laughs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEkarshi%2C%20whose%20first%20film%20this%20is%2C%20sets%20up%20the%20interpersonal%20dynamics%20within%20the%20group%20in%20an%20economical%20and%20brisk%20first%2025%20minutes.%20Vinay%20used%20to%20be%20the%20lead%20in%20the%20play%20before%20Hari%20joined%20the%20group%2C%20but%20since%20then%2C%20%5Bbecause%20of%20his%20popularity%5D%2C%20they%E2%80%99ve%20been%20doing%20more%20shows%20and%20more%20people%20are%20turning%20up%20to%20watch.%20Vinay%2C%20who%20is%20waiting%20for%20his%20divorce%20to%20come%20through%2C%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20told%20the%20group%20that%20he%20and%20Anjali%20are%20in%20love.%20Prasanth%20(Prasanth%20Madhavan)%20is%20in%20love%20with%20Anjali%2C%20and%20when%20he%20tries%20to%20express%20it%20to%20her%2C%20she%20rebuffs%20him.%20Sijin%20(Sijin%20Sijeesh)%20has%20a%20bone%20to%20pick%20with%20Anjali%2C%20because%20he%20heard%20she%20played%20a%20role%20in%20calling%20off%20his%20marriage%20to%20Anjali%E2%80%99s%20cousin.%20The%20elders%20in%20the%20group%20think%20of%20Anjali%20as%20her%C2%A0%20%E2%80%98daughter%2Fsister%E2%80%99%2C%20or%20at%20least%20that%E2%80%99s%20what%20they%20all%20say.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20morning%20after%20the%20celebration%20at%20the%20villa%2C%20Anjali%20is%20nowhere%20to%20be%20found.%20When%20Vinay%20tries%20to%20call%20her%2C%20she%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20pick%20up.%20A%20few%20days%20later%2C%20Anjali%20meets%20Vinay%20and%20tells%20him%20she%20was%20groped%20that%20night.%20She%20was%20asleep%20near%20a%20window%2C%20when%20she%20felt%20a%20hand%20come%20in.%20She%20managed%20to%20grab%20the%20person%E2%80%99s%20pocket%20and%20car%20keys%20fell%20out.%20She%20suspects%20it%20was%20Hari%20because%20the%20keys%20belong%20to%20him.%20Vinay%20is%20angry%2C%20and%20suggests%20Anjali%20inform%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20group%20so%20he%20can%20be%20expelled.%20Initially%2C%20Anjali%20is%20hesitant.%20But%20Vinay%20convinces%20her%20to%20let%20him%20approach%20Madan%20(Madan%20Babu)%20%E2%80%93%20the%20coordinator%20of%20the%20theatre%20group.%20He%20asks%20Madan%20to%20tell%20everyone%20that%20Anjali%20approached%20him%20with%20the%20complaint%2C%20and%20requests%20him%20to%20call%20the%20entire%20group%20to%20decide%20on%20Hari%E2%80%99s%20fate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%E2%80%99s%20where%20Ekarshi%E2%80%99s%20film%20%E2%80%93%20his%20tribute%20(and%20subversion)%20to%20Sidney%20Lumet%E2%80%99s%20iconic%20chamber%20drama%2C%20%3Cem%3E12%20Angry%20Men%3C%2Fem%3E%20(1957)%20%E2%80%94%20actually%20begins.%20Everyone%20in%20the%20theatre%20group%2C%20barring%20Hari%2C%20reaches%20Madan%E2%80%99s%20house.%20They%E2%80%99re%20informed%20about%20Anjali%E2%80%99s%20allegation%20against%20Hari%2C%20and%20it%E2%80%99s%20fascinating%20how%20each%20of%20them%20responds.%20There%E2%80%99s%20initial%20rage%20and%20disgust%20%E2%80%93%20someone%20casually%20says%20how%20he%E2%80%99ll%20lynch%20Hari%20the%20next%20time%20he%20sees%20him.%20Someone%20tries%20to%20ask%20basic%20questions%20%E2%80%93%20%E2%80%9CHow%20does%20she%20know%20it%20was%20Hari%3F%20Did%20she%20see%20him%3F%E2%80%9D%20One%20of%20them%20opines%20how%20the%20scandal%20could%20smear%20the%20name%20of%20the%20theatre%20group%2C%20and%20no%20women%20might%20want%20to%20join%20them%20in%20the%20near%20future.%20Someone%20talks%20about%20a%20compromise%20that%20needs%20to%20be%20reached%20between%20Hari%20and%20Anjali%2C%20while%20another%20one%20of%20them%20simply%20shuts%20down%20any%20talk%20about%20a%20compromise%2C%20stating%20unequivocally%20that%20they%20should%20just%20expel%20Hari%20and%20go%20public%20about%20it%20%E2%80%93%20it%E2%80%99s%20the%20only%20responsible%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20discussion%20in%20%3Cem%3EAattam%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20in%20many%20ways%2C%20mirrors%20our%20social%20media%20discourse.%20Most%20people%20tend%20to%20come%20from%20a%20place%20of%20pure%20intention%2C%20but%20with%20varying%20degrees%20of%20empathy%2C%20sensitivity%2C%20cultural%20biases%2C%20intellectual%2C%20and%20financial%20limitations.%20Just%20like%20everyone%20on%20social%20media%20is%20brought%20to%20believe%3A%20everyone%20has%20a%20right%20to%20an%20opinion.%20But%20are%20all%20opinions%20equally%20well%20thought-out%3F%20How%20many%20of%20us%20introspect%20when%20our%20core%20beliefs%20are%20challenged%20by%20someone%20more%20articulate%3F%20It%E2%80%99s%20exactly%20what%20happens%20when%20the%20characters%20in%20Ekarshi%E2%80%99s%20film%20%E2%80%93%20all%20coming%20from%20different%20walks%20of%20life%20%E2%80%93%20bring%20together%20an%20entire%20bouquet%20of%20thoughts%2Fopinions.%20Amidst%20all%20this%20talk%2C%20how%20quickly%20does%20the%20main%20point%20of%20contention%20recede%20into%20the%20background%3F%20Is%20anyone%20keeping%20track%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Lumet%E2%80%99s%20classic%20film%2C%20the%20contrarian%20is%20the%20hero.%20All%20jurors%20seem%20to%20be%20in%20a%20rush%20to%20pronounce%20their%20judgements%20and%20do%20away%20with%20the%20accused.%20However%2C%20the%20one%20who%20asks%20everyone%20to%20reconsider%20ultimately%20ends%20up%20swaying%20the%20room.%20In%20Ekarshi%E2%80%99s%20version%2C%20we%20see%20Sijin%20express%20his%20doubts%20in%20Anjali%E2%80%99s%20account.%20Only%20a%20scene%20later%2C%20his%20bias%20against%20Anjali%20%E2%80%93%20for%20breaking%20up%20his%20prospective%20marriage%20with%20her%20cousin%20%E2%80%93%20is%20revealed.%20Selvan%2C%20an%20elder%20in%20the%20group%2C%20calls%20Anjali%20his%20%E2%80%98daughter%E2%80%99%2C%20but%20follows%20it%20up%20with%20how%20she%20shouldn%E2%80%99t%20be%20drinking%20recklessly%20or%20dressing%20in%20a%20certain%20way.%20The%20group%20delves%20into%20details%20of%20Anjali%E2%80%99s%20account%2C%20relying%20on%20their%20memory%2C%20and%20tries%20to%20look%20for%20hints%20of%20guilt%20in%20their%20conversations%20with%20Hari%2C%20in%20the%20days%20after%20the%20celebration%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEkarshi%20introduces%20another%20delicious%20plot-point%2C%20where%20the%20group%20stands%20to%20gain%20a%20significant%20amount%20of%20money%20with%20their%20continued%20association%20with%20Hari%2C%20making%20even%20the%20most%20cocksure%20theatre%20group%20members%20wobble%20about%20their%20stance%20about%20expelling%20him.%20As%20Anjali%20is%20summoned%20by%20the%20group%2C%20and%20tiny%20inconsistencies%20emerge%20in%20her%20account%2C%20it%20takes%20only%20a%20few%20moments%20for%20all%20these%20%E2%80%9Callies%E2%80%9D%20to%20reconsider%20their%20stance.%20Most%20of%20the%20men%2C%20with%20their%20male-saviour%20complex%2C%20are%20revealed%20to%20be%20squabbling%20infants.%20Some%20are%20blinded%20by%20the%20riches%20they%20stand%20to%20gain%2C%20as%20against%20backing%20an%20imperfect%20victim%20with%20probable%20%E2%80%98holes%E2%80%99%20in%20her%20story.%20While%20the%20others%20are%20simply%20too%20egotistical%20to%20look%20beyond%20their%20biases%20and%20consider%20the%20cold%20facts%20of%20the%20case.%20Beyond%20a%20point%2C%20no%20one%E2%80%99s%20interested%20in%20learning%20what%20really%20happened%2C%20only%20the%20least%20obtrusive%20way%20to%20%E2%80%98move%20on%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAattam%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20the%20kind%20of%20chamber%20drama%20that%20one%20would%20liken%20to%20an%20action%20film%2C%20where%20characters%20fight%20with%20words%20%5Blike%20a%20Sorkin%20film%5D.%20Ideas%20are%20thrown%20at%20each%20other%2C%20and%20while%20there%E2%80%99s%20a%20chance%20that%20one%20is%20better%20than%20the%20other%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20more%20fascinating%20when%20both%20characters%20have%20a%20point.%20Real%20life%2C%20after%20all%2C%20is%20full%20of%20ambiguous%20circumstances%20that%20prod%20us%20to%20think%3A%20%E2%80%9CWhat%20would%20I%20have%20done%3F%E2%80%9D%20Barring%20Vijay%20Forrt%2C%20the%20others%20are%20relatively%20unknown%20on%20the%20screen%2C%20which%20is%20a%20good%20thing%2C%20because%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20any%20preconceived%C2%A0notions%20about%20the%20characters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20shown%20recently%20at%20the%20MAMI%20Film%20Festival%20and%20had%20earlier%20won%20an%20award%20at%20the%20Indian%20Film%20Festival%20in%20Los%20Angeles%20and%20will%20eventually%20be%20on%20an%20OTT%20platform.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMost%20Indian%20films%20haven%E2%80%99t%20been%20able%20to%20do%20justice%20to%20the%20nuances%20of%20the%20%23MeToo%20movement%2C%20or%20showcase%20the%20messy%20aftermath%20of%20a%20sexual%20harassment%20investigation.%20Ekarshi%E2%80%99s%20film%20seems%20to%20understand%20and%20closely%20observe%20the%20ignorance%20of%20the%20Indian%20man%2C%20who%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20learned%20sensitivity%20and%20is%20largely%20clueless%20about%20asking%20the%20%E2%80%98right%E2%80%99%20questions%20to%20an%20alleged%20victim.%20Amidst%20all%20this%2C%20%3Cem%3EAattam%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20sure%20about%20one%20thing%20though%3A%20most%20Indian%20men%20wanting%20to%20play%20%E2%80%98saviours%E2%80%99%20or%20%E2%80%98allies%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%93%20can%E2%80%99t%20handle%20the%20truth.%20And%20when%20they%20lose%20sight%20of%20it%2C%20nobody%20wins.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699704381000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F11173301%2FThe-Wire-75.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ffilm%2Fmalayalam-film-aattam-shows-how-the-truth-can-be-messy-and-complicated%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Anand%20Ekarshi%E2%80%99s%20debut%20weaves%20an%20intricate%20plot%20which%20is%20reminiscent%20of%20'12%20Angry%20Men'.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A10%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ffilm%2Fmalayalam-film-aattam-shows-how-the-truth-can-be-messy-and-complicated%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Netanyahu%20vows%20to%20press%20on%20with%20'full%20force'%20as%20'two%20babies%20die'%20after%20power%20runs%20out%20at%20Gaza's%20lar