99s%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%202023%20kicked%20off%20on%205%20October%2C%202023%2C%20with%20an%20inspiring%20and%20sustainable%20twist%20as%20Coca-Cola%20India%20%E2%80%94%20in%20collaboration%20with%20the%20International%20Cricket%20Council%20(ICC)%20%E2%80%94%20introduced%20a%20pioneering%20initiative%20in%20the%20world%20of%20cricket.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECelebrating%20the%20shared%20passion%20for%20the%20sport%20and%20a%20dedication%20to%20sustainability%2C%20Coca-Cola%20India%20and%20ICC%20unveiled%20national%20flags%20crafted%20from%20post-consumer%20PET%20bottles%2C%20making%20this%20global%20sporting%20event%20a%20platform%20for%20promoting%20environmental%20responsibility.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPET%20bottles%20were%20ingeniously%20transformed%20into%20yarn%2C%20which%20was%20then%20skillfully%20crafted%20into%20flags.%20These%20flags%20played%20a%20prominent%20role%20in%20the%20pre-match%20national%20anthem%20ceremony%20at%20stadiums%20throughout%20the%20tournament.%20Coca-Cola%20India%20oversaw%20the%20creation%20of%20national%20flags%20for%20all%2010%20participating%20nations%2C%20as%20well%20as%2010%20ICC%20unity%20flags.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20environmental%20initiative%20ushered%20in%20a%20new%20era%20of%20responsibility%20and%20sustainability%2C%20showcasing%20Coca-Cola%E2%80%99s%20commitment%20to%20a%20greener%20future.%20In%20doing%20so%2C%20Coca-Cola%20and%20ICC%20became%20the%20first%20companies%20worldwide%20to%20introduce%20recycled%20PET%20national%20flags%20to%20the%20game%20of%20cricket%2C%20setting%20a%20precedent%20for%20future%20sporting%20events.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CInnovation%20and%20sustainability%20take%20center%20stage%20at%20the%20ICC%20Men%E2%80%99s%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%202023%2C%20where%20national%20flags%2C%20embodying%20unity%2C%20and%20pride%2C%20are%20now%20crafted%20from%20recycled%20PET%20bottles.%20With%20Coca-Cola%20India%E2%80%99s%20collaboration%2C%20we%20have%20introduced%20a%20groundbreaking%20environmental%20initiative%2C%20symbolizing%20our%20collective%20pledge%20towards%20a%20more%20eco-friendly%20future%20and%20a%20sustainable%20sports%20culture%2C%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%20stated%20an%20%3Cstrong%3EICC%20Head%20of%20Events%2C%20Chris%20Tetley.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201024px)%20100vw%2C%201024px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FCocaCola_ICC_Ground_11zon-1699628770.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20ICC%20Men's%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%202023%20showcased%20environmental%20responsibility%20by%20unveiling%20national%20flags%20crafted%20from%20recycled%20PET%20bottles.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FCocaCola_ICC_Ground_11zon-1699628770.jpg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FCocaCola_ICC_Ground_11zon-1699628770-300x225.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FCocaCola_ICC_Ground_11zon-1699628770-500x375.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FCocaCola_ICC_Ground_11zon-1699628770-768x576.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FCocaCola_ICC_Ground_11zon-1699628770-150x113.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-334072%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22768%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20ICC%20Men%E2%80%99s%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%202023%20showcased%20environmental%20responsibility%20by%20unveiling%20national%20flags%20crafted%20from%20recycled%20PET%20bottles.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20bring%20these%20exceptional%20flags%20to%20life%2C%20approximately%2011%2C000%20PET%20bottles%20were%20used%20to%20create%20each%20national%20flag%2C%20while%20approximately%202%2C000%20PET%20bottles%20were%20utilised%20for%20each%20ICC%20unity%20flag.%20The%20flags%20were%20skillfully%20manufactured%20by%20GoRevise%20%E2%80%94%20a%20division%20of%20Ganesha%20Ecoverse%20Limited%20%E2%80%94%20which%20specialises%20in%20the%20production%20of%20recycled%20yarn%20and%20garments.%20Over%20100%20dedicated%20workers%20contributed%20their%20time%20and%20effort%2C%20working%20tirelessly%20for%2025%20days%20and%20clocking%20over%20300%20hours%20to%20produce%20these%20flags.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20thrilled%20to%20announce%20Coca-Cola%20India%20%E2%80%94%20partnering%20with%20the%20International%20Cricket%20Council%20in%20collaboration%20with%20Go%20Rewise.%20Together%2C%20we%20have%20made%20history%20at%20the%20ICC%20Men%E2%80%99s%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%202023%20by%20unveiling%20the%20National%20Flags%20of%20each%20country%20participating%20in%20the%20World%20Cup%20and%20the%20ICC%20Unity%20Flag.%20These%20flags%20are%20a%20first%20in%20cricket%20worldwide%2C%20made%20entirely%20from%20Recycled%20PET%20bottles.%20India%20is%20celebrating%2C%20and%20we%20at%20Go%20Rewise%20are%20equally%20delighted%20to%20be%20a%20part%20of%20this%20incredible%20moment%2C%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%20said%20%3Cstrong%3ESandeep%20Khandelwal%2C%20Vice%20President%2C%20Ganesha%20Ecosphere%20and%20Managing%20Director%2C%20Ganesha%20Ecoverse.%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECoca-Cola%20India%20initiated%20both-%20online%20and%20offline%20(on-ground)%20initiatives%20throughout%20the%20tournament%2C%20aimed%20at%20engaging%20fans%20and%20consumers%20and%20raising%20awareness%20about%20waste%20management.%20The%20Company%20is%20facilitating%20waste%20management%20as%20part%20of%20the%20%23MaidaanSaaf%20campaign%20and%20has%20installed%20reverse%20vending%20machines%20at%20all%20the%20stadiums%20for%20the%20collection%20of%20consumed%20PET.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EArnab%20Roy%2C%20Vice%20President%2C%20Marketing%2C%20Coca-Cola%20India%20%26amp%3B%20So