%20the%20Asian%20giant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlong%20with%20China%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mea.gov.in%2Fbilateral-documents.htm%3Fdtl%2F37252%2FJoint_Statement_Fifth_Annual_IndiaUS_22_Ministerial_Dialogue%5C%22%3Ethe%20joint%20statement%20on%20the%20%E2%80%982%2B2%E2%80%99%20talks%3C%2Fa%3E%20demonstrated%20their%20similar%20position%20on%20the%20Israel-Hamas%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNoting%20horrific%20terrorist%20attacks%20against%20Israel%2C%20the%20ministers%20reiterated%20that%20India%20and%20the%20United%20States%20stand%20with%20Israel%20against%20terrorism%20and%20called%20for%20adherence%20to%20international%20humanitarian%20law%2C%20including%20with%20regard%20to%20the%20protection%20of%20civilians%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20the%20bilateral%20document.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fby-siding-with-israel-india-is-jettisoning-decades-of-middle-east-statesmanship%5C%22%3EBy%20Siding%20With%20Israel%2C%20India%20Is%20Jettisoning%20Decades%20of%20Middle%20East%20Statesmanship%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECalling%20for%20the%20immediate%20release%20of%20all%20hostages%2C%20the%20joint%20statement%20further%20stated%20that%20the%20two%20sides%20were%20committed%20to%20%E2%80%9Ccontinue%20coordinating%20with%20partners%20in%20the%20region%20on%20humanitarian%20assistance%20to%20meet%20the%20urgent%20needs%20of%20Palestinian%20civilians%20in%20Gaza%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20and%20the%20US%20reiterated%20their%20support%20for%20%E2%80%9Chumanitarian%20pauses%E2%80%9D.%20This%20is%20a%20day%20after%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapnews.com%2Farticle%2Fisrael-gaza-humanitarian-pauses-b8fc613ffd8b9351c0dc37b90b6e10dd%5C%22%3EIsrael%20agreed%20to%20allow%20the%20halting%20of%20fighting%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20four%20hours%20every%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20expressed%20support%20for%20humanitarian%20pauses%20and%20committed%20to%20conti