%20cause%20of%20Madigas.%20In%20the%20past%2C%20it%20was%20mostly%20the%20leaders%20from%20opposition%20parties%20who%20attended%20the%20meetings%20organised%20by%20this%20rights-based%20body%20in%20the%20Telugu%20states%20to%20win%20the%20political%20support%20of%20Madigas%2C%20who%20constitute%20a%20majority%20among%20Dalit%20sub-groups%20in%20Telangana.%20Is%20the%20presence%20of%20Modi%2C%20in%20his%20capacity%20as%20prime%20minister%2C%20an%20acknowledgement%20by%20the%20Indian%20state%20of%20the%20demands%20that%20MRPS%20has%20been%20raising%3F%20Or%20does%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20see%20an%20inherent%20political%20opportunity%20to%20woo%20the%20Madigas%2C%20as%20well%20as%20various%20Dalit%20sub-groups%20across%20the%20country%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20moot%20question%20now%20is%20whether%20the%20prime%20minister%20accedes%20to%20the%20longstanding%20demand%20of%20MRPS%20and%20the%20Madigas.%20In%20the%20wake%20of%20impending%20elections%20in%20Telangana%2C%20it%20is%20to%20be%20seen%20if%20the%20BJP%20uses%20it%20to%20its%20advantage%20to%20counter%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20social%20justice%20politics%20at%20the%20national%20level%20by%20announcing%20Dalit%20sub-categorisation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20three-decade-old%20movement%20by%20the%20MRPS%20has%20foregrounded%20the%20problem%20of%20how%20some%20influential%20sections%20of%20the%20Dalit%20community%20disproportionately%20benefit%20from%20the%20Scheduled%20Caste%20reservations%20at%20the%20cost%20of%20others.%20To%20remedy%20this%2C%20MRPS%20has%20been%20pushing%20for%20what%20is%20called%20the%20%E2%80%98rationalisation%20of%20reservations%E2%80%99%2C%20or%20%E2%80%98categorisation%E2%80%99%2C%20to%20ensure%20each%20Dalit%20group%20gets%20to%20benefit%20from%20reservations%20commensurate%20with%20their%20population%20in%20their%20respective%20states.%20For%20instance%2C%20in%20Telugu%20states%2C%20Malas%20and%20Madigas%20are%20numerically%20preponderant%20Dalit%20sub-groups.%20In%20comparison%2C%20Malas%20are%20better%20off%20than%20Madigas%20in%20various%20aspects%2C%20due%20to%20various%20historical%20factors.%20They%20benefit%20disproportionately%20from%20reservations%20at%20the%20cost%20of%20Madigas%20and%20other%20less%20well-to-do%20Dalit%20subgroups.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20fight%20such%20disparities%20among%20Dalit%20sub-groups%2C%20MRPS%20was%20established%20on%20July%207%2C%201994%2C%20under%20the%20leadership%20of%20its%20founder-president%20Manda%20Krishna%20Madiga.%20Despite%20being%20a%20rights-based%20movement%2C%20it%20has%20since%20established%20itself%20on%20par%20with%20mainstream%20political%20parties%20with%20village-level%20committees%2C%20ground-level%20cadre%2C%20and%20a%20strong%20organisational%20network%20spread%20across%20various%20states.%20Any%20observant%20student%20of%20politics%20and%20rights-based%20movements%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20and%20Telangana%20can%20vouch%20for%20the%20MRPS%E2%80%99s%20standing%2C%20its%20reach%2C%20and%20its%20influence%20on%20social%20justice%20politics%20in%20the%20past%20three%20decades.%20During%20these%2030%20years%2C%20the%20movement%20has%20significantly%20influenced%20the%20discourse%20surrounding%20reservation%20categorisation%2C%20shaping%20the%20stances%20of%20political%20parties%2C%20and%20manifestos%20in%20favour%20of%20equitable%20distribution%20of%20the%20reservation%20pie%20among%20various%20caste%20groups.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20categorisation%20of%20Dalit%20sub-groups%20for%20reservation%20purposes%20remains%20unaddressed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20movement%20against%20historical%20injustice%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%201965%2C%20the%20B.N.%20Lokur%20Committee%2C%20constituted%20to%20revise%20the%20lists%20of%20Scheduled%20Castes%20and%20Scheduled%20Tribes%2C%20recommended%20to%20the%20government%20to%20remove%2014%20tribes%20and%2028%20castes%20from%20the%20hitherto%20existing%20SC%20and%20ST%20lists.%20Notably%2C%20it%20proposed%20the%20exclusion%20of%20the%20Mala%20caste%20group%20from%20Andhra%20Pradesh%2C%20highlighting%20its%20progress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%201996%20commission%20set%20up%20by%20the%20Andhra%20Pradesh%2C%20under%20the%20leadership%20of%20Justice%20P.%20Ramachandra%20Raju%2C%20also%20confirmed%20yawning%20disparities%20in%20the%20utilisation%20of%20reservations%20among%20Dalit%20sub-groups%2C%20recommending%20to%20the%20government%20categorisation%20of%20SCs%20based%20on%20their%20population%20for%20the%20purpose%20of%20reservations.%20It%20suggested%20that%20Dalits%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20be%20categorised%20into%20four%20groups%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20the%20level%20of%20backwardness%20and%20population.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBetween%202000%20and%202004%2C%20the%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20government%20moved%20to%20implement%20these%20recommendations.%20However%2C%20a%20counter-movement%20launched%20by%20the%20Mala%20community%20proved%20an%20impediment%20to%20Dalit%20sub-categorisation%2C%20culminating%20finally%20in%20a%20Supreme%20Court%20directive%20asking%20the%20government%20not%20to%20proceed%20forward.%20The%20court%20noted%20that%20the%20categorisation%20of%20reservations%20was%20only%20possible%20through%20a%20constitutional%20amendment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20seemed%20a%20victory%20for%20the%20MRPS%20was%20only%20short-lived%2C%20prompting%20the%20organisation%20to%20renew%20its%20struggle%20with%20more%20rigour%20by%20demanding%20successive%20governments%20to%20push%20for%20constitutional%20amendments%20by%20the%20Union%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Justice%20Usha%20Mehra%20Commission%20(2007)%2C%20constituted%20by%20the%20Union%20government%2C%20also%20proposed%20categorisation%20among%20Dalits%20to%20ensure%20fair%20distribution%20of%20reservation%20benefits.%20It%20suggested%20that%20the%20state%20government%20may%20invoke%20the%20enabling%20provision%20of%20Article%2016(4)%20of%20the%20constitution.%20This%20particular%20constitutional%20provision%20enables%20a%20state%20government%20to%20draw%20up%20a%20reservation%20plan%20for%20appointments%20and%20decide%20the%20extent%20of%20such%20reservations%20in%20proportion%20to%20the%20population%20of%20caste%20groups.%20To%20tide%20over%20any%20legal%20issues%2C%20the%20Committee%20suggested%20an%20amendment%20to%20Article%20341%20of%20the%20constitution%2C%20which%20empowers%20parliament%20to%20notify%20castes%20and%20tribes%20as%20Scheduled.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Commission%20further%20observed%20that%20Dalit%20sub-groups%20such%20as%20Madiga%2C%20Relli%2C%20and%20Adi-Andhra%20had%20been%20socially%20and%20economically%20disadvantaged%20and%20should%20be%20granted%20SC%20reservations%20as%20per%20their%20population%20among%20Dalit%20sub-groups.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20the%20issue%20of%20sub-classification%20among%20SCs%20and%20STs%20may%20not%20have%20received%20as%20much%20attention%20as%20the%20issue%20of%20sub-classification%20among%20OBCs%2C%20it%20has%20been%20entangled%20in%20a%20constitutional%20and%20legal%20battle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F08%2F24181353%2F11.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F08%2F24181353%2F11.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F08%2F24181353%2F11-300x169.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F08%2F24181353%2F11-1024x576.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-474913%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22675%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EIllustration%3A%20Pariplab%20Chakraborty.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20constitutional%20Bench%2C%20led%20by%20Justice%20Arun%20Mishra%2C%20in%202020%2C%20delivering%20its%20verdict%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findiankanoon.org%2Fdoc%2F137059642%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DThe%2520State%2520Government%2520cannot%2520exercise%2C16(4)%2520was%2520permitted.%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EState%20of%20Punjab%20vs%20Davinder%20Singh%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20aptly%20noted%20that%20reservation%20has%20created%20inequalities%20within%20the%20reserved%20castes%2C%20and%20noted%20that%20Dalit%20groups%20in%20the%20Scheduled%20Caste%20list%20should%20not%20be%20treated%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Chomogenous%20group%E2%80%9D.%20More%20importantly%2C%20it%20said%20states%20can%20sub-classify%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fsocialjustice.nic.in%2FUserView%2Findex%3Fmid%3D76750%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EScheduled%20Castes%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0and%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftribal.nic.in%2FST%2FLatestListofScheduledtribes.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EScheduled%20Tribes%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20Central%20List%20to%20provide%20preferential%20treatment%20to%20the%20%E2%80%9Cweakest%20out%20of%20the%20weak%E2%80%9D.%20The%20Central%20List%20of%20Scheduled%20Castes%20and%20Tribes%20is%20notified%20by%20the%20President%20under%20Articles%20341%20and%20342%20of%20the%20constitution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20adding%20or%20dropping%20any%20caste%2Ftribe%20from%20the%20List%20may%20need%20parliament%E2%80%99s%20approval%2C%20the%20bench%20noted%20preferential%20treatment%20to%20certain%20sections%20among%20reserved%20groups%20does%20not%20amount%20to%20%E2%80%9Ctinkering%E2%80%9D%20with%20the%20List.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fscheduled-castes-chinnaiah-arun-mishra-supreme-court%5C%22%3ESub-Classification%20of%20Scheduled%20Castes%3A%20Why%20the%20Chinnaiah%20Judgment%20Must%20Go%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20verdict%2C%20in%20effect%2C%20borrows%20from%20B.R.%20Ambedkar%E2%80%99s%20view%20of%20caste%20that%20no%20two%20castes%20are%20equal%20even%20if%20they%20were%20grouped%20under%20the%20overarching%20heading%20of%20Scheduled%20Castes%20and%20Tribes.%20Because%20caste%20constitutes%20a%20graded%20hierarchy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20same%20is%20reflected%20among%20Dalit%20sub-groups%20across%20the%20country.%20In%20the%20case%20of%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20and%20Telangana%20specifically%2C%20the%20Malas%20look%20down%20on%20the%20Madigas.%20This%2C%20in%20effect%2C%20translates%20into%20opportunities%20secured%20by%20Malas%20in%20comparison%20to%20Madigas%20in%20terms%20of%20education%20and%20employment%20through%20reservation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EHalf-hearted%20efforts%20of%20political%20parties%C2%A0%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ruling%20Bharat%20Rashtra%20Samithi%20(BRS)%2C%20in%20its%20avatar%20as%20Telangana%20Rashtra%20Samithi%2C%20asserted%20during%20the%20statehood%20movement%20that%20self-rule%20of%20Telangana%20primarily%20meant%20empowerment%20of%20its%20Dalit%20community%2C%20which%20had%20been%20neglected%20in%20the%20erstwhile%20united%20Andhra%20Pradesh.%20In%20advancing%20such%20a%20view%2C%20the%20BRS%20(then%20TRS)%20committed%20itself%20to%20the%20Dalit%20sub-categorisation%20in%20the%20new%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20assuming%20power%20in%202014%20in%20Telangana%2C%20the%20BRS%20government%20forwarded%20two%20resolutions%20passed%20in%20the%20Telangana%20assembly%20to%20the%20Union%20government%20pressing%20for%20Dalit%20sub-categorisation.%20In%20doing%20so%2C%20it%20has%20passed%20the%20buck%20on%20to%20the%20BJP-led%20Union%20government%20while%20also%20trying%20to%20win%20the%20trust%20of%20the%20Madiga%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%2C%20which%20had%20in%20the%20run-up%20to%20the%202014%20General%20Election%20promised%20to%20complete%20the%20classification%20of%20SC%20reservations%20within%20100%20days%20of%20assuming%20power%2C%20has%20still%20not%20honoured%20its%20commitment.%20The%20MRPS%20has%20been%20following%20it%20up%20with%20the%20Union%20government%20through%20several%20representations%20and%20delegations%20calling%20on%20the%20Union%20ministers.%20In%20November%202016%2C%20M.%20Venkaiah%20Naidu%2C%20in%20the%20capacity%20of%20Union%20minister%2C%20attended%20an%20MRPS%20meeting%20to%20reiterate%20his%20government%E2%80%99s%20commitment%20towards%20Madigas.%20However%2C%20seven%20years%20later%20the%20issue%20remains%20unresolved.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20regards%20the%20Congress%20party%2C%20its%20approach%20towards%20the%20issue%20has%20been%20further%20disappointing.%20The%20Congress%20government%20headed%20by%20Y.S.%20Rajashekar%20Reddy%20in%20the%20undivided%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20in%202009%20passed%20a%20similar%20resolution%20in%20the%20state%20assembly%20and%20led%20an%20all-party%20delegation%20to%20Delhi%20to%20press%20for%20Dalit%20sub-categorisation.%20However%2C%20nothing%20came%20of%20it.%20After%20the%20formation%20of%20Telangana%20state%20in%202014%2C%20the%20Congress%20state%20unit%20committed%20itself%20to%20deliver%20the%20long-standing%20demand%20of%20Madigas.%20The%20same%20is%20being%20reiterated%20by%20Congress%20this%20time%20around%20ahead%20of%20Telangana%20polls.%20Had%20Congress%20been%20committed%20to%20the%20issue%2C%20it%20should%20have%20delivered%20in%202009%20%E2%80%93%20when%20it%20was%20in%20power%20both%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20and%20at%20the%20Centre.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETherefore%2C%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20impending%20elections%20in%20Telangana%20and%20the%20foregrounding%20of%20social%20justice%20politics%20by%20the%20opposition%20at%20the%20national%20level%2C%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20scheduled%20speech%20at%20the%20MRPS%20meeting%20in%20Hyderabad%20assumes%20significance.%20From%20a%20political%20point%20of%20view%2C%20it%20could%20prove%20a%20potent%20move%20for%20the%20BJP%20to%20earn%20the%20support%20of%20the%20Dalit%20community%2C%20especially%20the%20Madigas%2C%20who%20are%20among%20the%20highest%20in%20number%20among%20Dalit%20sub-groups%20in%20Telangana.%20The%20Malas%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20have%20been%20traditionally%20associated%20with%20the%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20question%20is%20whether%20Modi%20greenlights%20Dalit%20sub-categorisation%2C%20or%20will%20he%20become%20part%20of%20the%20laundry%20list%20of%20political%20leaders%20who%20made%20promises%20but%20reneged%20on%20them%3F%20It%20is%20a%20matter%20of%20speculation.%20A%20favourable%20announcement%2C%20however%2C%20will%20mark%20a%20great%20victory%20not%20just%20for%20Madigas%2C%20less%20well-to-do%20Dalit%20sub-groups%2C%20and%20social%20justice%20politics%20but%20also%20for%20a%20grassroots%20people%E2%80%99s%20movement%20like%20the%20MRPS%20at%20a%20time%20when%20issue-based%20political%20mobilisations%20are%20facing%20unprecedented%20challenges.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ESuman%20Damera%20is%20an%20assistant%20professor%20at%20the%20Department%20of%20Public%20Administration%2C%20Pachhunga%20University%20College%20(PUC)%2C%20Mizoram%20University%2C%20Aizawl.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699615768000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F10110525%2FThe-Wire-72.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fhyderabad-modi-mrps-dalit-sub-categorisation%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20issue%20of%20disparities%20among%20Dalit%20sub-groups%20has%20long%20been%20discussed.%20The%20Madiga%20Reservation%20Porata%20Samithi%20has%20been%20pioneering%20sub-categorisation%2C%20but%20political%20parties%20of%20all%20colours%20have%20failed%20to%20make%20progress.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A33%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fhyderabad-modi-mrps-dalit-sub-categorisation%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Mughals%20or%20the%20Marathas%3A%20Who%20Invented%20Kaju%20Katli%2