com%2F333570%2Fsachin-nag-won-only-gold-medal-swimming-for-india-at-asian-games-sports-history%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20set%20day%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20guru%20walked%20out%20of%20prison%20with%20everyone%20holding%20onto%20the%20robe.%20Ironically%2C%20this%20day%20coincided%20with%20Diwali%20and%20came%20to%20be%20known%20as%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3EBandhi%20Chor%20Diwas%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%20to%20mark%20the%20liberation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEveryone%20acknowledged%20Guru%20Hargovind%E2%80%99s%20method%20as%20ingenious%20and%20Jehangir%E2%80%99s%20royal%20chef%20prepared%20a%20sweet%20to%20commemorate%20the%20day.%20The%20blend%20of%20cashew%20nuts%2C%20sugar%20and%20%3Cem%3Eghee%3C%2Fem%3E%20was%20relished%2C%20and%20needless%20to%20say%2C%20went%20down%20in%20history%20as%20a%20delicacy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20both%20versions%20reference%20their%20unique%20takes%20on%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F208578%2Fvegan-chocolate-dairy-free-cookies-healthy-cake-options-millet-recipes-order-online-lifestyle-tan42%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehistory%20of%20the%20sweet%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20you%20can%20go%20for%20the%20one%20you%20love.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699612900000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D333995%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Kaju%20Katli%20has%20conquered%20India%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98mithai%E2%80%99%20scene%2C%20but%20whose%20brainchild%20is%20it%3F%20History%20offers%20us%20two%20versions%20of%20how%20this%20sweet%20was%20created.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Krystelle%20Dsouza%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F333995%2Fdiwali-sweets-history-of-kaju-katli-barfi-mughals-maratha-chef-bhimrao%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22In%20Hyderabad%2C%20Policing%20of%20Teens%20Under%20%E2%80%98Operation%20Chabutra%E2%80%99%20Is%20Turning%20Violent%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F09165426%2FF9yZn8Ka0AEtKGZ.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20term%20that%20gained%20notoriety%20in%20Hyderabad%20recently%20is%20%E2%80%9Cchabutra.%E2%80%9D%20Contrary%20to%20the%20local%20population%E2%80%99s%20perception%20of%20a%20chabutra%20as%20a%20place%20of%20social%20gathering%2C%20it%20is%20perceived%20by%20the%20Hyderabad%20South%20Zone%20police%20as%20a%20place%20where%20youngsters%20indulge%20in%20illegal%20activities%20and%20criminal%20conspiracies%20late%20at%20night.%20This%20has%20led%20to%20a%20new%20form%20of%20policing%3A%20temporary%20detention%20of%20youngsters%20who%20step%20out%20after%20midnight%20in%20the%20city.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%202015%2C%20Sri%20Satyanarayan%20the%20deputy%20commissioner%20(DCP)%20of%20the%20South%20Zone%20police%20initiated%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FWLi-p0PRrBg%3Ffeature%3Dshared%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EOperation%20Romeo%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DHXRu_RB307I%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EOperation%20Chabutra%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20to%20discourage%20young%20individuals%20from%20gathering%20at%20chabutras%20and%20engaging%20in%20allegedly%20harmful%20activities.%20This%20practice%20was%20primarily%20aimed%20at%20raising%20awareness%20about%20the%20dangers%20of%20underage%20reckless%20bike%20riding%2C%20encouraging%20youngsters%20to%20use%20their%20time%20wisely%20and%20discouraging%20unnecessary%20late-night%20roaming%20that%20the%20police%20believed%20could%20potentially%20contribute%20to%20criminal%20activities.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EWhat%20is%20a%20chabutra%3F%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EChabutra%20is%20a%20colloquial%20term%20used%20in%20Hyderabad%20that%20refers%20to%20a%20raised%20platform%20or%20a%20pavement%20area%20typically%20found%20outside%20houses%20in%20residential%20areas.%20These%20structures%20often%20serve%20as%20community%20spaces%20for%20neighbours%20and%20residents%20to%20congregate%2C%20relax%2C%20or%20engage%20in%20conversations.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHistorically%2C%20chabutras%20have%20played%20an%20integral%20part%20in%20the%20city%E2%80%99s%20design%2C%20and%20cultural%20fabric%20and%20in%20fostering%20a%20sense%20of%20community%20and%20social%20interaction.%20The%20concept%20of%20a%20chabutra%20draws%20its%20inspiration%20from%20the%20traditional%20village%20settings%20in%20India%20where%20community%20members%20and%20elders%20would%20gather%20beneath%20a%20grand%20tree%20to%20engage%20in%20conversations%20and%20deliberate%20on%20matters%20concerning%20families%20and%20society.%20In%20many%20Indian%20villages%2C%20this%20platform%20also%20served%20as%20the%20assembly%20ground%20for%20the%20local%20panchayat%20to%20conduct%20their%20meetings.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20common%20practice%20in%20India%20to%20have%20small%20indoor%20and%20outdoor%20platforms%20within%20neighbourhoods%20where%20people%20sit%20and%20converse.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOver%20time%20this%20concept%20transformed.%20What%20was%20once%20a%20symbol%20of%20community%20bonding%20started%20to%20be%20associated%20with%20gatherings%20of%20youngsters%2C%20especially%20late%20in%20the%20night.%20These%20gatherings%20often%20involved%20socialising%2C%20chatting%2C%20and%20sometimes%20activities%20that%20raised%20concerns%2C%20including%20fights.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EWhy%20are%20chabutras%20targeted%20by%20the%20police%3F%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20police%20have%20been%20focusing%20their%20attention%20on%20chabutras%20due%20to%20a%20series%20of%20incidents%20in%20which%20conflicts%20between%20two%20groups%20or%20even%20disputes%20among%20friends%20escalated%20to%20tragic%20outcomes%2C%20including%20loss%20of%20life.%20These%20unfortunate%20incidents%20have%20raised%20concerns%20within%20the%20police%20force%20about%20night-time%20gatherings%20in%20the%20old%20city%20areas.%20Information%20provided%20by%20local%20media%20and%20police%20informants%20suggests%20a%20correlation%20between%20these%20gatherings%20and%20the%20occurrence%20of%20violent%20incidents.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETherefore%2C%20the%20police%20say%20they%20are%20laying%20more%20emphasis%20on%20ensuring%20that%20young%20individuals%20do%20not%20congregate%20in%20localities%20post-midnight.%20This%20%E2%80%9Cproactive%20approach%E2%80%9D%2C%20they%20say%2C%20aims%20to%20prevent%20confrontations%20and%20altercations%2C%20reduce%20the%20likelihood%20of%20violence%20and%20ultimately%20preserve%20public%20safety.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20police%E2%80%99s%20assumption%20that%20these%20gatherings%20could%20potentially%20lead%20to%20conflicts%20or%20illicit%20activities%20raises%20important%20questions.%20Indeed%2C%20there%20are%20instances%20of%20such%20gatherings%20causing%20disturbances%20to%20residents%20and%20also%20serving%20as%20locations%20for%20criminal%20activities.%20It%E2%80%99s%20crucial%20to%20recognise%20that%20within%20neighbourhoods%2C%20there%20are%20designated%20spots%2C%20often%20in%20alleyways%20or%20side%20streets%2C%20frequented%20by%20known%20troublemakers%20or%20individuals%20with%20criminal%20backgrounds.%20However%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20important%20to%20distinguish%20between%20these%20specific%20individuals%20and%20the%20broader%20community.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECan%20young%20people%20be%20prohibited%20from%20gathering%20with%20friends%3F%20Is%20it%20justifiable%20to%20curtail%20their%20freedom%20of%20peaceful%20assembly%20based%20on%20a%20few%20reported%20instances%20of%20crime%20in%20the%20old%20city%3F%20Does%20the%20law%20permit%20the%20detention%20and%20harassment%20of%20youth%2C%20simply%20for%20sitting%20outside%20their%20residences%3F%20These%20are%20critical%20questions%20that%20warrant%20thoughtful%20examination%20and%20consideration.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%E2%80%99s%20a%20positive%20aspect%20to%20chabutras%20that%20merits%20consideration.%20It%20has%20been%20observed%20that%20when%20residents%2C%20including%20youngsters%2C%20gather%20in%20their%20localities%2C%20it%20serves%20as%20a%20deterrent%20to%20crime%20and%20criminal%20activities.%20The%20presence%20of%20community%20members%20can%20discourage%20outsiders%20from%20attempting%20criminal%20acts%2C%20as%20they%20would%20be%20less%20likely%20to%20go%20unnoticed%20or%20unchallenged.%20This%20highlights%20the%20potential%20for%20chabutras%20to%20provide%20a%20space%20for%20social%20interaction%20%3Cem%3Eand%3C%2Fem%3E%20enhance%20security%20and%20cohesion%20in%20the%20neighbourhood.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETherefore%20a%20nuanced%20approach%20that%20addresses%20the%20concerns%20posed%20by%20gatherings%20that%20lead%20to%20disturbances%20and%20criminal%20behaviour%20while%20preserving%20the%20valuable%20role%20they%20can%20play%20in%20maintaining%20a%20safe%20and%20connected%20neighbourhood%20environment%20is%20necessary.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EPolice%20harassment%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20underlying%20motivation%20behind%20police%20operations%20in%20specific%20localities%20is%20complex%20and%20often%20influenced%20by%20various%20societal%20factors%2C%20including%20caste%2C%20class%2C%20and%20religious%20biases.%20To%20comprehend%20this%20intention%2C%20one%20must%20acknowledge%20the%20existing%20societal%20biases%20which%20shape%20the%20attitudes%20of%20government%20agencies%2C%20particularly%20the%20police.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHistorically%2C%20there%20has%20been%20a%20tendency%20to%20stereotype%20certain%20communities%20and%20areas%2C%20which%20subsequently%20impacts%20the%20orientation%20of%20law%20enforcement%20personnel.%20In%20the%20case%20of%20Hyderabad%E2%80%99s%20old%20city%2C%20it%20has%20often%20been%20portrayed%20as%20an%20area%20with%20potential%20criminal%20elements%2C%20extremists%2C%20and%20terrorists.%20The%20Muslim%20community%20which%20resides%20there%20has%20frequently%20faced%20police%20harassment%2C%20before%20and%20after%20the%20formation%20of%20Telangana.%20Muslim%20youth%20have%20been%20disproportionately%20targeted%20and%20detained%20in%20alleged%20terrorism%20cases%2C%20subjecting%20them%20to%20years%20of%20harassment%2C%20particularly%20following%20the%20Babri%20Masjid%20demolition.%20This%20biased%20perception%20is%20not%20accidental%3B%20rather%2C%20it%20is%20a%20deliberate%20part%20of%20the%20training%20and%20conditioning%20of%20law%20enforcement%20agencies.%20Muslims%20are%20often%20unfairly%20portrayed%20as%20radicalised%20and%20potential%20extremists%20or%20terrorists%2C%20contributing%20to%20a%20global%20narrative%20that%20emerged%20post-9%2F11%2C%20when%20international%20agencies%20began%20associating%20terrorism%20with%20the%20Muslim%20community.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20addition%20to%20the%20biases%20against%20Muslims%2C%20caste%20and%20class%20factors%20also%20influence%20the%20mindset%20of%20bureaucrats%20and%20law%20enforcement%20officers.%20There%20is%20a%20perception%20that%20individuals%20from%20backward%20communities%20with%20lower%20socioeconomic%20backgrounds%20are%20more%20likely%20to%20engage%20in%20criminal%20activities.%20This%20perception%20leads%20to%20the%20targeting%20of%20poor%20and%20vulnerable%20localities%20through%20measures%20such%20as%20cordon%20and%20search%20operations%20and%20%E2%80%98Mission%20Chabutra%E2%80%99.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EConversely%2C%20affluent%20and%20educated%20neighbourhoods%20often%20escape%20similar%20scrutiny.%20This%20imbalance%20in%20police%20operations%20reflects%20a%20broader%20societal%20bias%2C%20where%20individuals%20from%20disadvantaged%20backgrounds%20are%20disproportionately%20targeted%2C%20while%20those%20from%20privileged%20backgrounds%20enjoy%20relative%20impunity.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOperation%20Chabutra%20has%20been%20portrayed%20in%20a%20positive%20light%20by%20the%20police%20with%20the%20help%20of%20local%20media.%20But%20of%20late%2C%20there%20has%20been%20a%20surge%20of%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DjUat6S25AzY%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Evideos%20showing%20police%20using%20violent%20force%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20on%20youngsters%2C%20including%20instances%20of%20the%20police%20continuously%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FNewsMeter_In%2Fstatus%2F1715981167537930405%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ehitting%20teenagers%20with%20%3Cem%3Elathis%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20This%20escalation%20of%20violence%20on%20a%20large%20scale%20across%20an%20entire%20community%20of%20people%20is%20a%20dangerous%20trend%20emerging%20out%20of%20Hyderabad.%20While%20the%20local%20population%20initially%20supported%20a%20non-violent%20way%20of%20policing%20youth%2C%20they%20are%20increasingly%20concerned%20about%20this%20escalation.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20tragedy%20of%20this%20exercise%20is%20that%20instead%20of%20following%20the%20rule%20of%20law%2C%20the%20police%20have%20become%20the%20lawmakers%20in%20Hyderabad.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3ES.Q.%20Masood%20is%20a%20social%20activist%20from%20Hyderabad%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699612203000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F09165426%2FF9yZn8Ka0AEtKGZ.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fin-hyderabad-policing-of-teens-under-operation-chabutra-is-turning-violent%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20police%20have%20long%20seen%20the%20chabutras%20in%20Old%20City%2C%20a%20place%20for%20social%20gathering%2C%20as%20locations%20for%20youngsters%20to%20indulge%20in%20illegal%20activities%20late%20at%20night.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A7%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fin-hyderabad-policing-of-teens-under-operation-chabutra-is-turning-violent%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Goodbye%2C%20Range%20Anxiety!%20Now%20Convert%20Your%20Petrol%20Two-Wheeler%20Into%20a%20Hybrid%20EV%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20concept%20of%20sustainability%20gaining%20popularity%20and%20people%20increasingly%20interested%20in%20making%20eco-friendly%20choices%20to%20reduce%20their%20carbon%20footprint%2C%20India%20has%20witnessed%20a%20surge%20in%20innovations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20finding%20alternatives%20to%20single-use%20plastics%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F97000%2Fansoo-gupta-one-shoe-trust-responsible-tourism%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eresponsible%20tourism%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20India%20is%20experiencing%20a%20wave%20of%20cost-effective%20innovations%20in%20nearly%20every%20sector.%20Within%20the%20automobile%20industry%2C%20companies%20have%20introduced%20innovations%20in%20Electric%20Vehicles%20(EVs)%3B%20however%2C%20many%20consumers%20still%20express%20concerns%20over%20its%20battery%20life%2C%20with%20lingering%20anxiety%20about%20reaching%20a%20charging%20point%20or%20their%20destination%20before%20it%20runs%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Bengaluru%E2%80%99s%20Green%20Tiger%20Mobility%20employs%20a%20unique%20model%20which%20enables%20you%20to%20seamlessly%20transition%20between%20petrol%20and%20electric%20power%20within%20the%20same%20vehicle.%20To%20put%20it%20simply%2C%20the%20company%20converts%20your%20conventional%20petrol%20vehicle%20into%20a%20hybrid%20model%2C%20allowing%20it%20to%20operate%20on%20both%20petrol%20and%20electric%20batteries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20means%20that%20you%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20to%20worry%20about%20your%20battery%20running%20out%20mid-journey%3B%20you%20can%20easily%20switch%20to%20petrol.%20As%20the%20founder%2C%20Ashish%20Dokania%2C%20aptly%20puts%20it%20for%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%2C%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20like%20having%20two%20scooters%20in%20one.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20road%20to%20green%20mobility%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBorn%20and%20raised%20in%20a%20small%20town%20in%20Bihar%2C%20Ashish%20Donkaia%20had%20always%20been%20keen%20on%20building%20something%20on%20his%20own.%20Coming%20from%20a%20family%20of%20entrepreneurs%2C%20he%20says%20that%20the%20instincts%20were%20always%20there%2C%20but%20%E2%80%9CI%20wanted%20to%20become%20an%20entrepreneur%20who%20can%20make%20a%20difference%20in%20the%20society.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0At%20the%20young%20age%20of%2021%2C%20Ashish%20started%20a%20business%20in%20Bengaluru.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20very%20young%20and%20naive%20and%20could%20not%20really%20sustain%20it.%20I%20decided%20to%20close%20it%20down%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%20While%20the%20business%20had%20to%20be%20closed%2C%20it%20ignited%20a%20spirit%20in%20Ashish%20to%20run%20a%20successful%20business%20one%20day.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fev-1-1699540109.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20company%20has%20received%20ARAI%20%26amp%3B%20RTO%20approval%20to%20convert%20all%20major%20brands%20of%20scooters%20up%20to%20125cc.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fev-1-1699540109.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%